hadiths[254]{hadithnumber,text}:
2505,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamein khutba irshad farmaya : ''logo ! tum par Haj farz kar diya gaya hai lihaza tum Haj karo.'' kisi aadmi ne arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! kya her saal? aap khamosh rahey, yahan tak ke usney teen martaba kaha, phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar main haan keh deta to (phir her saal) wajib ho jata, aur tum istataat na rakhtay.'' phir farmaya : ''jab tak main tumhen koi masla na bataaun to mujhey chhodey rakho, tum se pehley log apney Anbiya se ziyada sawal karney aur un se ikhtilaf karney ki wajeh se halak huye, jab main kisi chiz ke barey main tumhen hukm dun to maqdoor (taqat) bhar is par amal karo aur jab main kisi chiz se tumhen mana karun to usey chhod do.'' rawahu Muslim."
2506,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se puchha gaya, kon sa amal afzal hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah aur uskey Rasool par eman lana.'' arz kiya gaya, phir kon sa? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ki raah mein jihad karna.'' arz kiya gaya, phir kon sa? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''hajje-maqbool.'' muttafaq aleh."
2507,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs Allah ke liye Haj karey, phir wo gunah ka kaam karey na fohsh-goi (gandi baat) karey to wo (gunahon se paak ho kar) us roz ki tarah laut'taa hai jis roz uski walida ne usey janm diya tha.'' muttafaq aleh."
2508,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Umra doosrey Umre tak ke darmiyani waqfa mein honey waley gunahon ka kaffara hai, aur hajje-maqbool ki jaza jannat hi hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
2509,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Ramazan mein Umra karna (sawab ke lihaz sey) Haj ke barabar hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
2510,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) rauhaa ke maqam par eik qafiley se miley to aapney puchha : ''kon ho?'' unhoney arz kiya, musalman. phir unhoney puchha : aap kon hain? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ka Rasool.'' eik aurat ne eik bachcha utha kar arz kiya : kya iska Haj hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''haan, aur tumharey liye uska ajr hai.'' rawahu Muslim."
2511,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain Khasam qabila ki eik aurat ne arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! Allah ka apney bandon par jo Haj ka fariza hai usney merey boodhey baap ko is haal mein paya ke wo sawari par sahih tarah beth nahin saktey , to kya main unki taraf se Haj karun? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''haan.'' aur ye Hajjatul-wadaa ke moqe par hua. muttafaq aleh."
2512,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik aadmi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to usney arz kiya : meri behan ne Haj karney ki nazar maana thi lekin wo faut ho chuki hain, to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar is par qarz hota to kya tum usey ada kartey?'' usney arz kiya, ji haan, to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''phir Allah ka qarz bhi ada karo, wo to adaegi ka ziyada haq daar hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
2513,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''koi aadmi kisi aurat ke sath khilwat (tanhaaee) ikhtiyar karey na koi aurat Mohrim ke baghair safar karey.'' eik aadmi ne arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! falan falan ghazwe mein mera naam likh liya gaya hai jabkey meri ehliya (biwi) Haj karney ka irada rakhti hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jaao aur apni ehliya ke sath Haj karo.'' muttafaq aleh."
2514,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se jihad par janey ki ijazat talab ki aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' tumhara jihad Haj hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
2515,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''koi aurat Mohrim ke baghair eik din aur eik raat ka safar na karey.'' muttafaq aleh."
2516,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ehale Madina ke liye zal-Hulaifa , ahle-Sham ke liye Johfa , ehle-Najad ke liye qarnul-manaazil aur ehle Yamen ke liye yalamlam ko meeqaat muqarrar kiya, wo unke liye hain aur unke ilawa un raaston se aaney walon ke liye hain jabkey wo Haj aur Umra ada karney ka irada rakhtey hon, aur jo un meeqaaton ke andar ki janib rehta hai to wo apney ghar se ehram baandheyga , aur is tarah aur is tarah yahan tak ke Makka waley Makka se ehram baandhengey.'' muttafaq aleh."
2517,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aur ehle Madina zal-Hulaifa ke maqam par ehram baandhen gey , jabkey doosrey raaston waley Johfa sey, ehle Iraq zaate-arq sey, ehle-Najad qarn se aur ehle-Yamen yalamlam se ehram baandhengey.'' rawahu Muslim."
2518,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne chaar Umerey kiye hain wo sab zul-Qada mein kiye, us Umre ke alawa jo aapney Haj ke sath kiya, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik Umra Hudebiya se zul-Qada mein kiya, eik Umra agley saal zul-Qada mein kiya, eik Umra Jaarana se jahan aapney Hunain ka maale-ghanimat taqseem kiya wo bhi zul-Qada mein aur eik Umra apney Haj ke sath kiya. muttafaq aleh."
2519,"Hazrat Bara bin Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Haj karney se pehley zul-Qada mein do umre kiye. Bukhari."
2520,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''logo ! Allah ne tum par Haj karna farz qarar diya hai.'' to Aqraa bin Habis (Raziallahu anhu) khadey huey aur arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! kya her saal? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar main haan keh deta to (her saal Haj karna) wajib ho jata, aur agar wajib ho jata to tum amal kartey na tum istataat rakhtey, aur Haj karna eik martaba farz hai, aur jo shakhs ziyada martaba karey to wo nafli hai.'' rawahu Ahmed, Nasai aur Darmi."
2521,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ke paas Baitullah tak pahunchney ke liye zaade-rah aur sawari ho wo phir bhi Haj na karey to phir is par koi farq nahin ke wo Yahudi ho kar faut ho ya nasrani , aur ye isliye hai ke Allah tabarak w taala farmata hai : '' aur jo shakhs Baitullah tak pahunchney ki istataat rakhta ho to is par Baitullah ka Haj karna wajib hai.'' Tirmizi . aur unhoney farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai iski asnaad par kalam kya gaya hai, jabkey Hilal bin Abdullah majhool hai aur Haris ko hadees mein zaeef qarar diya gaya hai. rawahu Tirmizi ."
2522,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Islam mein ''صرورہ'' ( gosha nasheenon ikhtiyar karna , shaadi na karna , istataat ke bawajud Haj na karna waghera) nahin hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
2523,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs Haj ka irada rakhta ho to wo jaldi karey.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood w Darmi ."
2524,"Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''hajj aur Umra pai dar pai (eik ke baad doosra ( karo, kyonkey wo faqr aur gunahon ko is tarah khatam kar detey hain jis tarah bhatti lohey, soney aur chaandi ki mail door kar deti hai. aur Haj maqbool ki jaza sirf jannat hi hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi w Nasai ."
2525,Hazrat Imam Ahmed aur ibne-Maja ne umr (Raziallahu anhu) se ( خبث الحدید ( tak riwayat kya hai. rawahu Ahmed w ibne-Maja.
2526,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik aadmi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to usney arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! Haj wajib honey ki shart kya hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' zaade-rah aur sawari.'' rawahu Tirmizi w ibne-Maja ."
2527,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik aadmi ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se masla puchha : haaji ki sift kya hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''paraa ganda , bikhrey huey baal aur mail kuchail.'' phir doosra aadmi khada hua aur arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! kon sa Haj afzal hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''buland aawaz se takbeerein kehna aur qurbani ka khoon bahana.'' phir eik aur khada hua to usney arz kiya, raastey se kya murad hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' zaade-rah aur sawari.'' Sharahus-sunnah , aur Imam ibne-Maja ne isey apni sunan mein riwayat kiya lekin unhoney aakhiri baat (raastey se kya murad hai?) zikr nahin ki. rawahu Al-Baghwi Sharahus-sunnah aur ibne-Maja."
2528,"Hazrat Abu-Rizeen Aqeeli (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey to arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! merey walid bahut boodhey hain, wo Haj aur Umerey ki istataat rakhtey hain na sawari kar saktey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''apney walid ki taraf se Haj aur Umra kar.'' Tirmizi, Abu-Dawud, Nasai. aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. rawahu Tirmizi, Abu-Dawood aur Nasai."
2529,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne kisi aadmi ko shubarma ki taraf se talbiya (labbaik) kehtey huey suna to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''shabarma kon hai?'' usney kaha : mera bhai hai ya mera koi qaribi hai. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tum ne khud Haj kiya hua hai?'' usney arz kiya : nahin, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''pehley apni taraf se Haj karo, phir shabarma ki taraf se Haj karna.'' rawahu Shafai, Abu-Dawood aur ibne-Maja."
2530,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ehle mashriq ke liye aqeeq ko meeqaat qarar diya. rawahu Tirmizi aur Abu-Dawood."
2531,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ehle Iraq ke liye zaate-arq ko meeqaat qarar diya. rawahu Abu-Dawood aur Nasai.
2532,"Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''jo shakhs masjide-Aqsaa se masjide-Haram ke liye Haj ya Umre ka ehram baandhey to uskey agley pichhley gunah maaf kar diye jatey hain ya uskey liye jannat wajib ho jati hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood aur ibne-Maja."
2533,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ehle Yamen Haj kartey to wo zaade-rah sath nahin letey they aur wo kehtey they ham tawakkul karney waley hain. lekin jab wo Makka pahunch jatey to phir logon se sawal kartey, tab Allah Taala ne aayat nazil farmaee : ''zaade-rah ley liya karo, aur behtareen zaade-rah taqwa hai.'' Bukhari."
2534,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, maine arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! kya aurton par jihad farz hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : haan , un par jihad farz hai lekin un mein qitaal nahin, aur wo jihad Haj aur Umra hai.'' rawahu ibne-Maja."
2535,"Hazrat Abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ko koi zahiri hajat (zaade-rah aur sawari ki adam dastyaabi) ya zalim badshah ya (safar sey) rokney wala marz, Haj se na rokey aur wo phir bhi Haj kiye baghair faut ho jaey to phir agar wo chahey to Yahudi ho kar marey aur agar chahey to nasrani ho kar.'' rawahu Darmi."
2536,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Hajj aur Umra karney waley, Allah ke taqarrub ka qasd (irada) karney waley hain. agar wo us se dua karen to wo unki dua qubul farmaai aur agar wo us se maghfirat talab karen to wo unhen bakhsh dey.'' rawahu ibne-Maja."
2537,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''teen qism ke log, Mujahid, haaji aur Umra karney waley, Allah ke taqarrub (qurbat) ka qasd (irada) (iraada) karney waley hain.'' rawahu Nasai aur al-Behaqi."
2538,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum haaji se milo to usey salam karo, us se musaafa karo aur is se pehley ke wo apney ghar mein dakhil ho. us se darkhast karo ke wo tumharey liye maghfirat talab karey, kyonkey uski maghfirat ho chuki hai (aur aisey shakhs ki dua qubul hoti hai).'' rawahu Ahmed."
2539,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs Haj ya Umre ya jihad karney ke liye rawana ho, phir wo uskey raastey mein (amal karney se pehley) faut ho jaey to Allah uskey liye jihad karney waley, Haj karney waley aur Umra karney waley ka ajr ata farmata hai.'' (rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan)."
2540,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko, aap ke ehram baandhney se pehley , khushbu lagaya karti thi, aur isi tarah jab tawaf (ifaaza) se pehley ehram khol detey to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko kastoori ki khushbu lagaya karti thi goya main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki mang mein jabkey aap haalate-ehram mein they, khushbu ki chamak dekh rahi hun. muttafaq aleh."
2541,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko talbiya kehtey huey suna, jabkey aap baal jamaey huey they, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farma rahey they : ''main hazir hun, aey Allah ! main hazir hun, aap ka koi shareek nahin, be-shak her qism ki tareef , tamam nematen aur badshahat terey hi liye hai aur tera koi shareek nahin.'' aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) in kalimaat mein koi izafa nahin kartey they. muttafaq aleh."
2542,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apna paaon rikaab mein rakh letey aur aap ki oontni aap ko lekar sidhi khadi ho jati to aap Zul-Hulaifa ki masjid ke paas talbiya pukartey. muttafaq aleh."
2543,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath (Hajj ke liye) rawana huey to ham buland aawaz se Haj ka talbiya pukartey they. rawahu Muslim."
2544,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main Abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ke peechhey sawari par Sawar tha aur wo (Sahaba kiraam) Haj aur Umre ka ikhatta talbiya keh rahey they. Bukhari."
2545,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, ham Hajjatul-wadaa ke saal Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath rawana huey. ham mein se kisi ne Umre ka talbiya pukara , kisi ne Haj aur Umre ka aur kisi ne Haj ka talbiya pukara, jabkey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Haj ka talbiya pukara. jisney Umerey ka talbiya pukara tha usney ehram khol diya, aur jinhonne Haj ya Haj aur Umra dono ka ehram baandha tha to unhoney das zul-hijja tak ehram na khola. muttafaq aleh."
2546,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Hajjatul-wadaa ke moqe par Haj ke sath Umra milaya tha, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne pehley Umerey ke liye talbiya kaha aur phir Haj ke liye. muttafaq aleh."
2547,Hazrat Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke aapney ehram baandhney ke liye apna libas utara aur ghusl kiya (phir ehram baandha). rawahu Tirmizi aur Darmi.
2548,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ghusl ki chizon (khitmi aur gond waghera) se apney sar ke baalon ko jamaya. rawahu Abu-Dawood.
2549,"Hazrat khallad bin Saaib apney walid se riwayat kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Jibrael (Alaihissalam) merey paas tashrif laye to unhoney mujhey farmaya ke main apney Sahaba ko buland aawaz se talbiya pukarney ka hukm dun.'' rawahu Malik, Tirmizi, Abu-Dawood, ibne-Maja aur Darmi."
2550,"Hazrat Sehal bin Saad bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab koi musalman talbiya pukarta hai to uskey daain aur baain zamin ke aakhiri kinaron tak tamam pathar, tamam darkht aur mitti ke tamam dheley talbiya pukartey hain.'' rawahu Tirmizi aur ibne-Maja."
2551,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Zul-Hulaifa ke maqam par do rakatein padhtey , phir Zul-Hulaifa ki masjid ke paas oontni aap ko lekar sidhi khadi ho jati to aap in kalimaat ke sath talbiya pukartey : ''main hazir hun, aey Allah ! main hazir hun, tamam sa'adatein aur bhalaiyan terey haathon mein hain, main hazir hun, raghbat aur talabe-khair teri hi taraf hai aur amal terey hi liye hain.'' Bukhari, Muslim. aur alfaze-hadees Muslim ke hain. muttafaq aleh."
2552,Hazrat Umaara bin Khuzaima bin Sabit apney walid se aur wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain ke jab aap talbiya se farigh hotey to Allah se uski razamandi aur jannat ka sawal kartey aur uski rehmat ke zariey jahannam se bachaaw ki darkhast kartey they. rawahu Shafai.
2553,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Haj karney ka irada farmaya to logon mein aelan kiya, wo ikhattey ho gaey, jab aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ''baida''  ke maqam par tashrif laye to ehram baandha. Bukhari."
2554,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, mushrik kaha kartey they : ham hazir hain, tera koi shareek nahin, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farmatey : ''tum par afsos hai, bas-bas itna hi kaho.'' (phir wo mushrik kehtey) magar tera wo shareek hai jis ka to Malik hai aur (us chiz ka bhi to Malik hai) jis ka wo Malik hai. aur wo Baitullah ka tawaf kartey waqt ye kaha kartey they. rawahu Muslim."
2555,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Madina mein nau saal qiyam farmaya aur us doran Haj na kiya, phir daswin saal aapney logon mein Haj ka aelan karaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Haj ka irada rakhtey hain, bahut se log Madina pahunch gaey, ham aap ke sath rawana huey yahan tak ke ham Zul-Hulaifa pahunchey to Asma binte-Umais (Raziallahu anhu) ne Muhammad bin Abi Bakr (Raziallahu anhu) ko janm diya, unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko pegham bheja ke ab main kya karun? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ghusl kar, kapdey ka langot baandh kar ehram baandh ley.'' Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne (Zul-Hulaifa) masjid mein Namaz padhi phir (oontni) qaswaa par Sawar huey yahan tak ke jab aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki oontni aap ko lekar Beda par sidhi khadi ho gaee to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne tauheedi talbiya pukara : ''main hazir hun, her qism ki hamd , tamam nematen aur badshahat teri hai, tera koi shareek nahin.'' Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ham ne to sirf Haj ki niyat ki thi, hamein Umre ka pata nahin tha, yahan tak ke ham aap ke sath Baitullah mein pahunchey , to aapney Hajre-Aswad ko choomaa , saat chakkar lagaey , teen mein ramal kiya (zara akad kar daudey) aur chaar mein chaley , phir aap maqame Ibrahim par aaye to ye aayat padhi : ''maqame Ibrahim ko jaey Namaz banaao.'' aapney wahan do rakatein padhein aur maqame Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) ko apney aur Baitullah ke darmiyan rakha. aur eik dusri riwayat mein hai ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne pehli rakaat mein Sura Kaafirun aur dusri mein Sura Ikhlas padhi. phir aap Hajre-Aswad ke paas aaye aur usey choom kar darwazey se nikal kar Safa ki taraf tashrif ley gaey, jab aap Safa ke qarib pahunchey to ye aayat tilawat farmaai : ''safa aur Marwa Allah ki nishaniyon mein se hain, main wahin se shuru karunga jahan se Allah Taala ne shuru kiya, isliye aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Safa se shuru kiya aur is par chadh gaey yahan tak ke aapney Baitullah dekha, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) qibla rukh huey to Allah ki tohid aur kibriyaai bayan ki aur farmaya : ''Allah ke siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin, wo yakta hai, uska koi shareek nahin, usi ki badshahat hai aur usi ke liye her qism ki hamd qaabil hai. aur wo her chiz par qadir hai, Allah ke siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin, wo yakta hai, usney apna wada pura farmaya , apney bandey ki nusrat farmaee , aur us akeley ne lashkaron ko shikast di.'' phir aapney is doran dua farmaee, aapney ye kalimaat teen martaba farmaey. phir aap nichey utrey aur Marwa ki taraf gaey yahan tak ke jab aap wadi ke nasheb (dhaal) mein tezi se utarney lagey to aap daudney lagey yahan tak ke jab aap chadhney lagey to aap mamool ke mutabiq chaltey gaey yahan tak ke aap Marwa par pahunch gaey aur aapney wahan bhi wesay hi kiya jaisey Safa par kiya tha, yahan tak ke jab aap aakhiri chakkar mein pahunchey to aap Marwa par they aur Sahaba aap ke nichey they, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne wahan se aawaz detey huey farmaya : ''jis chiz ka mujhey ab pata chala hai agar uska mujhey pehley pata chal jata to main qurbani ka janwer sath na lata aur main is (Hajj) ko Umre mein tabdeel kar leta , jis shakhs ke paas qurbani ka janwer nahin wo ehram khol dey , aur usey Umre mein badal daley.'' Suraqa bin Malik bin Jaasham (Raziallahu anhu) khadey huey aur arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! kya ye is saal ke liye ya hamesha ke liye hai? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney eik haath ki ungliyan doosrey haath ki ungliyon mein dakhil kin aur do martaba farmaya : ''Umra Haj mein dakhil ho gaya, aur ye sirf hamarey isi saal ke liye hi nahin balke hamesha hamesha ke liye hai.'' Ali (Raziallahu anhu) Yamen se Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki qurbani ke liye oont lekar tashrif laye to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne un se poochhaa : ''jab tum ne Haj ki niyat ki thi to kya kaha tha?'' unhoney arz kiya : maine kaha tha : aey Allah ! main usi chiz ka talbiya pukarta hun jis ka terey Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne talbiya pukara hai. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kyonkey merey sath qurbani ka janwer hai lihaza tum ehram na kholo.'' raawi bayan kartey hain, qurbaniyon ke janweron ki wo jamaat jo Ali (Raziallahu anhu) Yamen se laye they aur wo jinhen Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sath lekar aaye they (ye sab) eik sau they. raawi bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aur un Sahaba jinkey paas qurbani ke janwer they, ke siwa sab logon ne ehram khol diye aur baal katar liye, jab tarwiya (aath zul-hijja) ka din hua to unhoney Mina ka irada kiya aur Haj ke liye ehram baandha, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apni oontni par Sawar huey, aapney wahan ( Mina mein) Zohar, Asr, Maghrib, Isha aur Fajr ki namazein padhin, phir thodi der qiyam farmaya yahan tak ke Suraj tulu ho gaya, aapney namra mein baalon ka bana hua khema laganey ka hukm farmaya, isliye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) rawana huey, Quraish ko is baat mein koi shak nahin tha ke aap Quraish ke dastoore jahiliyat ke mutabiq mashar haram (muzdalfa) mein waquf farmaain gey, lekin Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) wahan se guzar kar maidane Arafat mein tashrif ley gaey aapney dekha ke namra mein aap ke liye khema laga diya gaya hai, aap wahan utrey yahan tak ke Suraj dhal gaya to aapney (apni oontni) qaswaa ke barey mein hukm farmaya to is par paalaan rakh diya gaya, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) wadi ke nasheb (dhaal) (wadi urnaa) mein tashrif laye aur logon ko khitab kartey huey farmaya : ''be-shak tumhara khoon , tumhara maal tum (eik doosrey) par isi tarah haram hai jis tarah tumharey aaj ke din ki, is mahiney ki aur tumharey is shehar ki hurmat hai. sun lo ! jahiliyat ki her chiz merey paaon taley raund di gaee hai, jahiliyat ke khoon (yani qatl) bhi khatam kar diye gaey aur hamarey khoon mein se pehla khoon jisey main khatam kar raha hun wo Rabeea bin Haris ke bete ka khoon hai, aur wo bano Saad qabiley mein doodh pi raha tha ke qabila huzail ne usey qatl kar diya, aur jahiliyat ka sood khatam kar diya gaya, aur hamarey sood mein se pehla sood jisey main khatam kar raha hun wo Abbas bin Abdul-Muttalib (Raziallahu anhu) ka hai, wo mukammal taur par khatam hai, aurton ke barey mein Allah se dartey raho , tum ne unhen Allah ki amaan aur ehad ke sath hasil kiya hai, aur Allah ke kalimey ke zariey unhen halal kiya hai, un par tumhara haq ye hai ke wo tumharey bistar (maskan) par kisi aisey shakhs ko na aaney den, jisey tum napasand kartey ho, lekin agar wo aisey karen to phir tum unhen halki si zarab maar saktey ho, aur main tum main eik aisi chiz chhodey ja raha hun agar tum ne usey mazbooti se thaamey rakha to phir tum gumrah nahin hongey, aur wo hai Allah ki kitab. aur tum se merey mutalliq puchha jaeyga to tum kya kaho gey?'' unhoney arz kiya : ham gawahi detey hain ke aapney pahuncha diya, haq ada kar diya aur khair-khahi farmaee. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne angusht shahadat ko aasman ki taraf uthaya aur usey logon ki taraf jhukaatey huey teen martaba farmaya : ''aey Allah ! gawah rehna , aey Allah ! gawah rehna.'' phir Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ne Azan di aur phir iqaamat kahi to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Zohar padhaai, phir iqaamat kahi to aapney Asr padhaai, aur aapney in dono (namazon) ke darmiyan koi Namaz na padhi, phir aap sawari par Sawar huey yahan tak ke waquf ki jagah par tashrif ley gaey, aapney apni oontni qaswaa ka pet chattano ki janib kiya, aur Jabal mashaa pahaad (pedal chalney walon ki raah mein waqey reteele toodey) ko apney samney kiya, aur qibla rukh musalsal waquf farmaya yahan tak ke Suraj ghurub honey laga , thodi si zardi reh gaee yahan tak ke Suraj ki tikiya ghayeb ho gaee , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Usama (Raziallahu anhu) ko peechhey bithaya aur wahan se chaley yahan tak ke Muzdalfa tashrif ley aaye, aapney wahan eik Azan aur do iqaamat se Maghrib aur Ishaa ki namazein padhein aur in dono ke darmiyan koi nafl Namaz nahin padhi, phir aap let gaey yahan tak ke Fajr padhi, phir qaswaa par Sawar huey aur mashar haram tashrif laaye, qibla rukh ho kar us (Allah) se dua ki uski takbir aur tahleel aur tohid bayan ki, aap musalsal khadey rahey yahan tak ke khub ujala ho gaya, aap tulu aaftaab se pehley wahan se chal diye, aapney Fazal-bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ko apney peechhey sawar kiya aur aap wadi mohsir pahunchey to sawari ko thoda sa tez kiya, phir darmiyani raastey par ho liye jo ke jamara uqba par nikalta tha, yahan tak ke aap us jamara ke paas pahunchey jiskey paas darkht tha, aapney usey saat kankariyaan maarin, aap her kankari ke sath Allahu-Akbar kehtey they, un mein se her kankari aisi thi jisey chutki mein lekar chalaya ja sakta tha, aapney ye kankariyaan wadi ke nasheb (dhaal) se maareen, phir aap qurban gaah tashrif ley gaey, aapney tiresath (63) oont apney daste Mubarak se zibeh kiye, phir aapney ye fariza Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ko saunp diya to baqi oont unhoney zibeh kiye , aur aapney unhen bhi apni qurbani mein shareek kiya, phir aapney hukm farmaya aur her oont se eik eik tukda kaat kar handiya mein dal kar pakaya gaya, aap dono ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aur Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu)) ne us gosht mein se kuchh khaya aur uska shorbaa piya. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sawari par Sawar huey aur tawafe ifaaza kiya, namaze-Zohar Makka mein padhi, phir aap bano Abdul-Muttalib ke paas tashrif ley gaey jo zam zam pila rahey they, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Abdul-Muttalib ki aulad, pani nikalo, agar ye andesha na hota ke tumharey pani pilaney ke is kaam mein log tum par ghalib aa jaeyngey to main bhi tumharey sath pani kheenchtaa.'' unhoney aap ko eik dol pani diya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne is mein se nosh farmaya. rawahu Muslim."
2556,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Hajjatul-wadaa ke moqe par ham Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath rawana huye, ham mein aisey they jinhon ne Umre ke liye ehram baandha , aur ham mein baaz ne Haj ke liye ehram baandha , jab ham Makka pahunchey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ne Umre ke liye ehram baandha aur wo qurbani ka janwer sath nahin laya to wo ehram khol dey aur jis shakhs ne Umre ke liye ehram baandha aur wo qurbani ka janwer sath laya hai to wo Umerey ke sath Haj ke ehram ki niyat kar lein , phir wo ehram na kholey yahan tak ke wo in dono se farigh ho jaey.'' aur eik dusri riwayat mein hai : ''wo ehram na kholey yahan tak ke apni qurbani se farigh ho jaey, aur jis shakhs ne Haj ka ehram baandha tha to wo apna Haj mukammal karey.'' wo farmati hain, mujhey haiz aa gaya lihaza maine Baitullah ka tawaf kiya na Safa Marwa ki saee ki, aur main Arfa ke din (no zul-hijja) tak haalate-haiz mein rahi, maine to Umre ke liye ehram baandha tha, lekin Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey farmaya ke main apney sar ke baal khol kar kanghi karun aur Haj ke liye ehram baandhon, aur main Umra tarak kar dun.'' maine aisey hi kiya yahan tak ke maine apna Haj pura kiya, phir aapney (merey bhai) Abdur-Rehman bin Abi Bakr (Raziallahu anhu) ko merey sath bheja aur mujhey hukm farmaya ke main apney Umerey ki jagah tan'eem se Umra karun. aap (Raziallahu anhu) bayan karti hain, jin logon ne Umre ke liye ehram baandha tha unhoney Baitullah ka tawaf kiya aur Safa Marwa ki saee ki, phir unhoney ehram khol diya, phir unhoney Mina se wapis aaney ke baad eik tawaf kiya, rahey wo log jinhonne Haj aur Umra ikhatta kiya to unhoney eik hi tawaf kiya. muttafaq aleh."
2557,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Hajjatul-wadaa ke moqe par Haj ke sath Umra milaya tha, aap Zul-Hulaifa se qurbani ka janwer apney sath ley gaey they, aapney pehley Umre ka ehram baandha , phir Haj ka ehram baandha, to Sahaba kiram (Raziallahu anhu) ne bhi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath Haj ko Umerey ke sath mila kar faeyda hasil kiya, kuchh log aisey bhi they jo qurbani ke janwer apney sath lekar gaey aur un mein se kuchh aisey bhi they jo qurbani ke janwer sath nahin laye they, jab Nabi Makka pahunchey to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne logon se farmaya : ''tum mein se jo shakhs qurbani ka janwer sath laya hai to uskey liye koi chiz halal nahin jo is par haram thi yahan tak ke wo apna Haj pura kar ley , aur jo shakhs qurbani ka janwer sath nahin laya to wo Baitullah ka tawaf karey, Safa Marwa ki saee karey, baal katwaa kar ehram khol dey, phir (hajj ke moqe par) Haj ke liye ehram baandhey, aur qurbani karey, to jo shakhs qurbani ka janwer na paey to wo teen rozey Haj ke dinon mein aur saat rozey apney ghar pahunch kar rakhey.'' jab aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Makka pahunchey to aapney tawaf kiya aur sab se pehley Hajre-Aswad ko choomaa, phir aapney teen chakkar daud kar lagaey aur chaar chakkar mamool ki chaal chal kar lagaey, jab aap tawaf mukammal kar chukey to aapney maqame Ibrahim ke paas do rakatein padhin, phir aapney Safa aur Marwa ke darmiyan saee ke saat chakkar lagaey, phir aap par un chizon mein se koi bhi chiz halal nahin hui thi jo aap par haram thi yahan tak ke aapney apna Haj mukammal kiya aur qurbani ke din qurbani ki aur Baitullah shareef pahunch kar tawafe ifaaza kiya, phir aap ke liye wo tamaam chizen halal ho gaeen jo aap par haram huin thin, aur jo log qurbani ke janwer sath laye they unhoney bhi wesay hi kiya jaisey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne kiya. Muttafaq aleh."
2558,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye Umra hai jis se ham ne faeyda uthaya, aur jis shakhs ke paas qurbani ka janwer na ho to uskey liye tamam chizen halal hongi, kyonkey Umra roze-qiyamat tak ke liye Haj mein dakhil ho chuka hai.'' rawahu Muslim."
2559,"Hazrat Ata (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ko apney sath bahut se logon mein suna, unhoney farmaya : ham Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke Sahaba ne sirf akeley Haj hi ka ehram baandha tha, Ata bayan kartey hain, Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) chaar zul-hijja ko Makka tashrif laye to aapney hamein ehram kholney ka hukm farmaya : Ata bayan kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ehram khol do aur apni biwiyon ke paas jaao.'' Ata (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne is baat (aurton ke paas janey) ko un par wajib qarar nahin diya tha, balke un (aurton) ko unke liye mabaah (jayez) qarar diya tha. ham ne arz kiya, hamarey maidane Arafat mein janey mein sirf paanch din baqi reh gaey, to aapney hamein apni biwiyon ke paas janey (yani jima karney) ka hukm farmaya, aur jab ham maidane Arafat pahunchein to (goya ke) hamari sharm-gahen mani gira rahi hon. Ata (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) apney haath se ishara kar rahey they goya main un ke haath ke isharay ko dekh raha hun ke wo usey harkat dey rahey hain, raawi bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ham mein khadey huey to farmaya : ''tum jantey ho ke main tum sab se ziyada Allah se darta hun, tum sab se ziyada sachcha aur tum sab se ziyada neku-kaar hun, agar merey sath meri qurbani ka janwer na hota to main bhi tumhari tarah ehram khol deta, agar wo baat jo mujhey ab malum hui hai wo pehley malum ho jati to main qurbani ka janwer sath na lata , tum ehram khol do.'' to ham ne ehram khol diya aur ham ne samia' aur itaat ikhtiyar ki, Ata bayan kartey hain, Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sadqaat ki wasuli ke baad wahan (Makka) pahunchey to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum ne kis niyat se ehram baandha tha?'' unhoney arz kiya : jis niyat se Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ehram baandha tha, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne un se farmaya : ''qurbani karna aur haalate ehram mein raho.'' raawi bayan kartey hain, Ali (Raziallahu anhu) apney liye qurbani ka janwer sath laye they. Suraqa bin Malik bin Jaasham (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! kya ye isi saal ke liye hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''hamesha ke liye hai.'' rawahu Muslim."
2560,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke unhoney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) chaar ya paanch zul-hijja ko Makka pahunchey they, aap merey paas tashrif laye to aap ghusse ki haalat mein they. maine arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! aap ko kis ne naraz kiya hai? Allah usey jahannam mein dakhil farmaai , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tumhen malum nahin ke maine logon ko eik kaam ka hukm diya hai jabkey wo sankoch ka shikar hain. jis chiz ka mujhey ab pata chala hai agar uska mujhey pehley pata chal jata to main qurbani ka janwer apney sath na lata yahan tak ke main usey yahan se khareeda leta , phir main bhi ehram khol deta jaisey unhoney ehram khola hai.'' rawahu Muslim."
2561,"Hazrat Naafe bayan kartey hain ke ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) Makka mein dakhil honey se pehley wadi zii-tuwa mein raat basar kartey , subah ko ghusl kartey aur Namaz padh kar din ke waqt Makka mein dakhil hotey , aur jab aap wahan se nikaltey to bhi wadi-zii tuwa ke paas se guzartey, wahan raat basar kartey aur bayan kartey ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) isi tarah kiya kartey they. Muttafaq aleh."
2562,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Makka tashrif laye to aap uskey baalai (upri) hissey ki taraf se dakhil huey aur uskey nashebi (dhaali wale) hissey ki taraf se nikley they. Muttafaq aleh.
2563,"Hazrat Urwa bin Zuber bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Haj kiya to Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne mujhey bataya ke jab aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Makka tashrif laye to aapney sab se pehley wuzu kiya, phir Baitullah ka tawaf kiya, phir usey Umra (ka tawaf) na banaya, phir Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne Haj kiya to unhoney bhi sab se pehley tawaf kiya, phir unhoney bhi usey Umra na banaya , phir umr (Raziallahu anhu) aur phir Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ne bhi isi tarah kiya. Muttafaq aleh."
2564,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Haj ya Umre ka tawaf kartey to aap sab se pehley teen chakkar daud kar lagatey aur chaar chakkar chal kar lagatey they, phir aap do rakatein padhtey aur Safa aur Marwa ki saee farmatey they. Muttafaq aleh."
2565,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Hajre-Aswad se Hajre-Aswad tak teen chakkar tez chal kar lagaey aur chaar chakkar aam raftaar se chal kar lagaey , aur jab aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Safa aur Marwa ke darmiyan saee kartey to aap sailab ke bahaaw wali jagah par tez chaltey they. rawahu Muslim."
2566,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Makka tashrif laye to aap Hajre-Aswad ke paas aaye to usey bosa diya, phir aap apni daain janib par chaley to teen chakkar tez chal kar chaar chakkar aam raftaar se chal kar lagaey. rawahu Muslim."
2567,"Hazrat Zuber bin Arbi (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, kisi aadmi ne Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) se Hajre-Aswad ko bosa deney ke barey mein puchha to unhoney farmaya : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko usey haath lagatey aur bosa detey huey dekha hai. Bukhari."
2568,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko sirf do rukn Yamani (Hajre-Aswad aur rukn Yamani) ko chhotey huey dekha hai. Muttafaq aleh."
2569,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Hajjatul-wadaa ke moqe par oont par Sawar ho kar tawaf kiya, aap chhadee ke sath Hajre-Aswad ko chhotey they. muttafaq aleh."
2570,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne oont par Sawar ho kar Baitullah ka tawaf kiya jab aap Hajre-Aswad ke paas aatey to aap apney haath mein mojud kisi chiz ke sath ishara kartey aur Allahu-Akbar kehtey. Bukhari.
2571,"Hazrat Abu-Tufail (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko Baitullah ka tawaf kartey aur aap ke paas jo chhadi thi uskey sath Hajre-Aswad ko chhotey huey dekha aur aap chhadi ko bosa detey they. rawahu Muslim."
2572,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, ham Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath sirf Haj ke iraday se rawana huye, jab aap maqame-sarf par pahunchey to mujhey haiz aa gaya, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) merey paas tashrif laye to main ro rahi thi, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''shayad ke tumhen haiz aa gaya hai?'' maine arz kya, ji haan ! aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye to eik aisi chiz hai jo Allah ne Adam (Alaihissalam) ki betiyon par muqaddar kar diya hai, tum jab tak haiz se paak nahin ho jatin, Baitullah ke tawaf ke siwa deegar hajiyon ki tarah umur (baton) adaa karti raho.'' Muttafaq aleh."
2573,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne us Haj mein , jis mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen Hajjatul-wadaa se pehley Ameere-Hajj bana kar bheja tha, mujhey eik jamaat ke sath bheja aur hukm diya ke '' logon mein aelan kar diya jaey ke sun lo ! is saal ke baad koi mushrik Baitullah ka Haj karey na koi barahna (nangi) haalat mein Baitullah ka tawaf karey.'' Muttafaq aleh."
2574,"Hazrat Muhajir Makki (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se us aadmi ke barey mein puchha gaya jo Baitullah ko dekh kar haath uthata hai, unhoney farmaya : ham ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath Haj kiya to ham is tarah nahin kartey they. rawahu Tirmizi aur Abu-Dawood."
2575,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (Madina sey) rawana huye, jab aap Makka mein dakhil huey to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Hajre-Aswad ki taraf aaye usey bosa diya, phir Baitullah ka tawaf kiya, phir Safa par aaye to uskey ooper chadh gaey yahan tak ke Baitullah nazar aaney laga to aap haath utha kar jis qadr chaha , Allah ka zikr aur duayen kartey rahey. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
2576,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Baitullah ka tawaf Namaz ki tarah hai, albatta tum is mein baat waghera kar letey ho, jo shakhs us doran baat karey to wo sirf khair aur bhalai ki baat karey.'' Tirmizi, Nasai , Darmi. Imam Tirmizi (Raziallahu anhu) ne muhaddeseen ki eik jamaat ka zikr kiya hai, jinhonne isey ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) par moquf qarar diya hai. rawahu Tirmizi, Nasai aur Darmi."
2577,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Hajre-Aswad jannat se nazil hua tha to wo doodh se bhi ziyada safed tha lekin aulade Adam ki khataaon ne usey siyah kar diya.'' Ahmed, Tirmizi. aur unhoney farmaya : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. rawahu Ahmed aur Tirmizi."
2578,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Hajre-Aswad ke barey mein farmaya : ''Allah roze-qiyamat usey uthaeyga to uski do aankhen hongi jin se wo dekhega aur zaban hogi jis se wo boleyga , aur jisney haq ke sath usko bosa diya hoga uskey haq mein gawahi dega.'' rawahu Tirmizi, ibne-Maja aur Darmi."
2579,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''Hajre-Aswad aur maqame Ibrahim (wo pathar jis par khadey ho kar aapney Baitullah ki taamir ki) jannat ke do yaqoot hain, Allah Taala ne unke Noor ko khatam kar diya, aur agar wo unke Noor ko khatam na karta to wo dono mashriq aur maghrib ke beech ko roshan kar detey.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
2580,"Hazrat Ubaid bin Umer se riwayat hai ke ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) Hajre-Aswad aur rukne-Yamani par bahut ziyada ghalba kartey they, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke kisi eik sahabi ko un par ghalba kartey huey nahin dekha, unhoney farmaya : main isliye aisey karta hun ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''un dono ko haath lagana gunahon ka kaffara hai.'' aur maine aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''jo shakhs her haftey Baitullah ka tawaf karey aur uski hifazat karey to wo aisey hai jaisey usney ghulam azad kiya ho.'' aur maine aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''jab wo  (tawaf mein) eik qadam rakhta hai aur doosra uthata hai to Allah Taala uskey badley main eik gunah maaf kar deta hai aur uskey liye eik neki likh deta hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
2581,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Saaib (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko Hajre-Aswad aur rukne-Yamani ke darmiyan ye dua kartey huey suna : ''hamarey parwardigar ! hamein duniya mein bhalai ata farma aur aakhirat mein bhalai ata farma aur hamein aag ke azab se bacha.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
2582,"Hazrat Safiya binte Sheba (Raziallahu anhu) bayan karti hain, Abu-Tijaara ki beti (Habiba (Raziallahu anhu)) ne mujhey bataya ke main Quraish ki baaz aurton ke sath khandan Abu-Husain ke ghar gaee taake ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko Safa Marwa ke beech saee kartey huey dekhen, maine aap ko saee kartey huey dekha aur saee ki shiddat ki wajeh se aap ka izaar bikhar raha tha, aur maine aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''saee karo kyonkey Allah Taala ne saee karna tum par farz kar diya hai.'' Sharahus-sunnah, aur Imam Ahmed ne kuchh ikhtilaf ke sath riwayat kiya hai. rawahu Sharahus-Sunnah aur Ahmed."
2583,"Hazrat Qudama bin Abdullah bin Ammar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko Safa Marwa ke darmiyan oont par saee kartey huey dekha, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) kisi ko maartay na hataatey aur na kehtey ke hat jaao , raasta chhod do. Hasan Yaati rawahu Sharahus-Sunnah."
2584,"Hazrat Yala bin Umayya (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne sabz (hara) rang ki chadar se iztibaa (yani daayan kandhaa nangaa) karkey Baitullah ka tawaf kiya. rawahu Tirmizi, Abu-Dawood, ibne-Maja aur Darmi."
2585,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aur aap ke Sahaba ne Jaarana se Umra kiya to unhoney teen chakkar tez tez chal kar purey kiye aur unhoney apni (ehram ki) chaadaron ko (daahini) baghlon ke nichey se nikal kar apney baain kandhon ke ooper dal rakha tha. rawahu Abu-Dawood.
2586,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine jab se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko Hajre-Aswad aur rukne-Yamani ka istilaam (chhuna) kartey huey dekha hai tab se ham ne tangi ya aasani kisi bhi haal mein in ka istilaam karna nahin chhoda. Muttafaq aleh."
2587,"Hazrat Sahih Bukhari aur Sahih Muslim ki riwayat mein hai : Naafe bayan kartey hain, maine ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ko dekha ke wo apney haath se Hajre-Aswad ko chhotey phir haath choomtey , aur unhoney farmaya : maine jab se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko aisey kartey huey dekha hai tab se maine isey tarak nahin kiya. Muttafaq aleh."
2588,"Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, maine apni bimari ke barey mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se shikayat ki to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum Sawar ho kar logon ke peechhey peechhey tawaf karo.'' maine tawaf kiya jabkey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Baitullah ki eik janib (Baitullah ki deewar ke sath) Namaz padh rahey they aur aap Sura taur ki tilawat farma rahey they. Muttafaq aleh."
2589,"Hazrat Aabis bin Rabeea bayan kartey hain, maine umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko dekha ke aap (Raziallahu anhu) Hajre-Aswad ko bosa dey rahey hain aur farma rahey hain : main khub janta hun ke to eik patthar hai, to nafe aur nuqsan ka Malik nahin. agar maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko tujhey bosa detey huey na dekha hota to main tujhey kabhi bosa na deta. Muttafaq aleh."
2590,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''is rukne-Yamani par sattar farishtey maamoor hain, jo shakhs kehta hai : aey Allah ! main tujh se duniya aur aakhirat mein aafiyat ki darkhast karta hun, hamarey parwardigar ! hamein duniya mein bhalai ata farma , hamein aakhirat mein bhalai ata farma aur hamein aag ke azab se bacha. to wo farishtey Aameen kehtey hain.'' rawahu ibne-Maja."
2591,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs Baitullah ke saat chakkar lagaey aur us doran Subhanallah . . . . . . . . illa billah'' Allah paak hai, her qism ki tareef Allah ke liye hai, Allah ke siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin, Allah sab se bada hai, gunah se bachna aur nek amal karna mehaz Allah Taala ki tofiq ke sath hai.'' ke siwa koi baat na karey to uskey das gunah maaf kar diye jatey hain, uskey liye das nekiyan likhi jati hain aur uskey das darjaat buland kar diye jatey hain. aur jo shakhs tawaf karey aur us doran baaten karey to wo us haal mein aisey hai ke uskey paaon to rehmat mein hain (lekin ooper ka hissa rehmat mein nahin) jaisey kisi ne apney paaon pani mein dubo rakhey hon.'' rawahu ibne-Maja."
2592,"Hazrat Muhammad bin Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke unhoney Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se daryaft kiya, jabkey wo dono meena se Arafat ja rahey they, aap Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath us roz kaisey (takbir aur tahleel ( kiya kartey they? unhoney farmaya : ham mein se koi talbiya padhta to is par koi aetraz nahin tha aur ham mein se koi Allahu-Akbar kehta to is par bhi koi aetraz nahin tha. muttafaq aleh."
2593,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''maine (meena mein) us jagah qurbani zibeh ki hai jabkey meena sarey ka sara qurban gaah hai aur maine yahan waquf kiya hai jabkey maidan Arafat sarey ka sara waquf ki jagah hai aur maine yahan waquf kiya hai jabkey Muzdalfa sarey ka sara waquf ki jagah hai.'' rawahu Muslim.
2594,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah baqi dinon (din) ki nisbat Arfa ke din , sab se ziyada apney bandon ko jahannam se azadi ata farmata hai. aur wo qarib hota hai, phir unki wajeh se farishton par fakhr karta hai aur farmata : ye log kya chahtey hain?'' rawahu Muslim."
2595,"Hazrat Amr bin Abdullah bin Safwan apney mamu Yazid bin Sheban se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha : ham ne maidane Arafat mein aisi jagah waquf kiya jo ke baqaul unke Imam ke waquf ki jagah se bahut door tha, ibne Mirbbaa Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) hamarey paas aaye to unhoney kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey tumhari taraf qaasid bana kar bheja hai, wo tumhen farmatey hain : ''tum apni jagah par thehrey raho , kyonkey tum apney baap Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) ki meeras par ho.'' rawahu Tirmizi, Abu-Dawood, Nasai aur ibne-Maja."
2596,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''maidane Arafat purey ka pura waquf ki jagah hai, pura meena qurban gaah hai, pura Muzdalfa waquf ki jagah hai, aur Makka ke tamam raastey , raastey aur qurban gaah hain.'' (yani Makka aaney waley ke liye kisi bhi raastey se Makka mein dakhil hona jayez hai) rawahu Abu-Dawood aur Darmi."
2597,"Hazrat Khalid bin Hauza (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko Arfa ke din oont ki dono rikaabon mein paaon rakh kar khadey ho kar logon se khitab kartey huey dekha. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
2598,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib apney baap se aur wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Arfa ke din ki dua behtareen dua hai aur maine aur mujh se pehley anbiya (Alaihissalam) ne jo behtareen dua ki hai wo ye hai : ''Allah ke siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin, wo yakta hai, uska koi shareek nahin, uskey liye badshahat hai aur uskey liye her qism ki tareef hai, aur wo her chiz par qadir hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
2599,Hazrat Imam Maalik (Raziallahu anhu) ne Talha bin Ubaidullah se (la-shareek-lah) tak riwayat kiya hai. rawahu Maalik.
2600,"Hazrat Talha bin Ubaidullah bin Kurez (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''shetan Arfa ke din sab se ziyada haqeer , sab se ziyada nikaala hua, sab se ziyada zaleel aur sab se ziyada ghussay mein hota hai aur wo aisi haalat mein isliye hota hai ke wo nuzoole-rehmat aur kabeera gunahon ki maghfirat hotey huey dekh raha hota hai, albatta ghazwae Badr ke moqe par bhi usey is kaifiyat mein dekha gaya.'' kaha gaya Badr ke din usney kya dekha? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kyonkey usney Jibrael (Alaihissalam) ko farishton ki saf bandi kartey huey dekha tha.'' Imam Maalik ne mursal riwayat kiya hai, aur Sharahus-sunnah mein Masaabeh ke alfaz mein marwi (bayan) hai. rawahu Malaik aur Sharahus-sunnah."
2601,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab Arfa ka din hota hai to Allah aasmane-duniya par nuzool farmata hai aur in (Arafat mein waquf karney walon) ki wajeh se farishton par fakhr karta hai aur farmata hai : merey bandon ko dekho kis tarah bikhrey baalon , ghubar aalud paaon aur buland aawaz se pukartey huey door daraz se aaye hain. main tumhen gawah bana kar kehta hun ke maine unhen bakhsh diya. to farishtey arz kartey hain, rab ji ! falan banda to burey kaam kiya karta tha, aur falan mard aur falan aurat bhi, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Shan Walla Allah farmata hai : ''maine unhen bakhsh diya hai.'' Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Arfa ke din ke siwa koi aisa din nahin jis mein Arfa ke din se ziyada logon ko jahannam se azadi milti ho.'' rawahu Sharahus-sunnah."
2602,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Quraish aur unke ham Deen log Muzdalfa mein qiyam kiya kartey they, aur unhen teiswin kaha jata tha, jabkey baqi sab Arab Arfa mein waquf kiya kartey they, jab Islam aaya to Allah Taala ne apney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko hukm farmaya ke wo Arafat ayen aur wahan waquf karen aur phir wahan se wapis ayen. isi tarah Shan Wale Allah ka farman hai : ''phir tum bhi wahan se lauto jahan se aam log laut'tey hain.'' muttafaq aleh."
2603,"Hazrat Abbas bin Mirdas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Arafat mein teharte huey apni ummat ki maghfirat ke liye dua farmaee to qubuliyat ka jawab aaya ke ''maine huqooq-ul-ibaad ke siwa baqi sab gunah maaf kar diye , kyonkey main us se mazloom ka haq lunga.'' aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne arz kiya : ''rab ji ! agar aap chahen to mazloom ko jannat ata kar den aur zalim ko bakhsh den.'' lekin us qiyam mein aap ki dua qubul na hui, to jab Muzdalfa mein subah ki to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne dua dohraai to aap ki dua qubul kar li gaee. raawi bayan kartey hain : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hansey ya tabassum farmaya to Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kiya : merey waliden aap par qurban hon ye to aisa waqt hai ke is waqt aap hansa nahin kartey they, aap ko kis chiz ne hansaayaa , Allah Taala aap ko khush aur khurram rakhey, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah ke dushman iblees ko jab pata chala ke Shan Wale Allah ne meri dua qubul farma kar meri ummat ko bakhsh diya hai to wo apney sar mein mitti dalney laga aur tabahi aur halakat ko pukarney laga, jab maine uski be sabri dekhi to mujhey hansi aa gaee.'' rawahu ibne-Maja aur al-Behaqi."
2604,"Hazrat Hisham bin Urwa apney walid se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha : Usama bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha gaya ke Hajjatul-wadaa ke moqe par wapsi ke waqt Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) kis tarah chaltey they? unhoney farmaya : aap osat raftaar se chaltey they aur jab kushada jagah aa jati to phir tez ho jatey they. muttafaq aleh."
2605,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Arfa ke din wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath wapis aa rahey they ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney peechhey oonton ko bahut maarney aur daantne ki aawazen sunin to aapney apney kodey se unki taraf ishara kiya aur farmaya : ''logo ! sakeenat ikhtiyar karo kyonkey sawaariyon ko tez daudaanaa koi neki nahin.'' Bukhari.
2606,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Arafat se Muzdalfa tak Usama bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu), Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke peechhey bethey they, phir aapney Muzdalfa se Mina tak Fazal-bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ko apney peechhey bitha liya , un dono ne bayan kiya hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jamara Aqba ko kankariyaan maarney tak talbiya pukartey rahey. muttafaq aleh."
2607,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Maghrib aur Ishaa ki namazein Muzdalfa mein ikhatti padhein aur her Namaz ke liye iqaamat kahi, aapney un dono namazon ke darmiyan koi nafl Namaz padhi na un mein se kisi ke baad. Bukhari."
2608,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko , Muzdalfa mein do namazon , namaze-Maghrib aur Ishaa ko jama karney aur usi roz namaze-Fajr ko uskey waqt se pehley padhney ke siwa , hamesha namazon ko unke oqaat mein padhtey huey dekha. muttafaq aleh."
2609,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main bhi un logon mein se hun jinhen Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Muzdalfa ki raat apney ehle khana ke zaeef afrad ke sath pehley (Mina) rawana kar diya tha. muttafaq aleh."
2610,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu), Fazal-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain ke wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke peechhey sawari par Sawar they ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Arfa ki Sham aur Muzdalfa ki subah logon sey, jabkey wo wapis aa rahey they, farmaya : ''aaram se aao.'' jabkey aap apni oontni ko (tez chalney sey) rok rahey they, yahan tak ke aap wadi mohsir mein dakhil ho gaey jo ke Mina ke qarib hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jamara ki rami karney ke liye chhoti chhoti kankariyaan ley lo.'' raawi bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jamara ko kankariyaan maarney tak talbiya pukartey rahey. rawahu Muslim."
2611,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Muzdalfa se wapis tashrif laye to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) par sakeenat aur itminan tha, aur aapney Sahaba ko bhi aaram se chalney ka hukm farmaya, jabkey wadi mohsir mein aap tez chaley aur unhen hukm farmaya ke ungli par rakh kar maari janey wali kankari ke barabar kankariyaan maaro, aur farmaya : ''shayad is saal ke baad main tumhen na dekh sakoon.'' maine ye hadees taqdeem aur takheer ke sath Jaame Tirmizi ke ilawa sahe-hain mein nahin pai. rawahu Tirmizi, Abu-Dawood, Nasai aur ibne-Maja."
2612,"Hazrat Muhammad bin Qais bin Makhrima bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne khutba irshad farmaya to farmaya : ''ehale jahiliyat Arafat se us waqt lauta kartey they jab Suraj ghurub honey se pehley is tarah ho jaisey aadmiyon ki pagadiyaan unke chehron par hon, aur Muzdalfa se tulu aaftaab ke baad jaisey aadmiyon ki pagadiyaan unke chehron par hon. jabkey ham ghurub aaftaab ke baad Arafat se laut'tey hain aur tulu aaftaab se pehley Muzdalfa se wapis aatey hain, hamara tariqa , buton ke pujaariyon aur mushrikon ke tareeqey se mukhtalif hai.'' Behaqi. aur farmaya : hamein khutba irshad farmaya, aur baqi hadees wesay hi bayan ki. (rawahu al-Behaqi)."
2613,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamein Muzdalfa ki raat bano abdul-Muttalib ke bachchon ke sath gadhon par bitha kar pehley hi rawana kar diya tha, aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) piyaar se hamari raanon par maar rahey they aur farma rahey they : ''merey piyarey bachcho ! jab tak Suraj tulu na ho jaey jamara ko kankariyaan na maarna.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood, Nasai aur ibne-Maja."
2614,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ko qurbani ki raat hi bhej diya tha, unhoney Fajr se pehley hi jamara ko kankariyaan maar li thin, phir wo (Mina sey) chali gaeen aur tawafe ifaaza kiya, aur ye wo din tha jis din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) unke yahan they. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
2615,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, muqeem (makkey ka rehney wala) ya Umra karney wala Hajre-Aswad ke istilaam tak talbiya pukarta rehta tha. Abu-Dawood. aur farmaya : aur ye Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) par moquf riwayat ki gaee hai. rawahu Abu-Dawood aur Tirmizi."
2616,Hazrat Yaqoob bin Aasim bin Urwa se riwayat hai ke unhoney Shareed (Raziallahu anhu) ko bayan kartey huey suna ke main Arafat se Muzdalfa tak Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath wapis aaya to Muzdalfa pahunchney tak aap ke qadam Mubarak zamin par nahin lagey. (yani aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sawari par aaye) rawahu Abu-Dawood.
2617,"Hazrat ibne-Shahab bayan kartey hain, Salim ne mujhey bataya ke jis saal Hujjaj bin yousuf, ibne-Zubair ke madde-muqaabil aaya to usney Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) se masla daryaft kiya, ham Arfa ke din waquf mein (namazon ka ( kya keren? Salim ne kaha : agar tum sunnat ki ittiba karna chahtey ho to phir Arfa ke din Namaz ko jaldi padho, Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya usney sach kaha hai, wo Zohar aur Asr ko sunnat ke mutabiq hi jama kiya kartey they. maine Salim se puchha : kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne aisey kiya? to Salim ne kaha : wo (Sahaba (Raziallahu anhu)) aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki sunnat hi ki ittiba kartey hain. Bukhari."
2618,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine qurbani ke din Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko , apni sawari par bethey huey kankariyaan maartey dekha, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farma rahey they : ''tum apney Haj ke tareeqey seekh lo, kyonkey main nahin janta ke shayad main apney is Haj ke baad Haj na kar sakoon.'' rawahu Muslim."
2619,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko chutki mein lekar chalai janey wali kankari ke barabar kankariyaan maartay huey dekha. rawahu Muslim."
2620,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne qurbani ke din chaasht ke waqt kankariyaan maarin, jabkey uskey baad Suraj dhal janey ke baad maaren. muttafaq aleh."
2621,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke wo jamara kubraa (badey shetan) ke paas pahunchey, Baitullah ko apni daain janib aur Mina ko apni baain janib rakha aur saat kankariyaan maarin, wo her kankari ke sath Allahu-Akbar kehtey they, phir unhoney farmaya : jis zaate-aqdas par Sura Baqra nazil hui thi, unhoney bhi isi tarah kankariyaan maarin thin. muttafaq aleh."
2622,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''istinje ke liye dheley istimal karney ki tadaad taaq hai, kankariyaan maarna taaq hai, safa, Marwa ke darmiyan saee taaq hai aur tawaf taaq hai, jab tum mein se koi istinje ke liye dheley istimal karey to wo taaq adad mein dheley istimal karey.'' rawahu Muslim."
2623,"Hazrat Qudama bin Abdullah bin Ammar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko qurbani ke din apni surkhi maael safed oontni par beth kar kankariyaan maartey huey dekha, wahan kisi ko roka ja raha tha na hataayaa ja raha tha aur na hi ye kaha ja raha tha ke hat jaao padhi. ! hat jaao ! rawahu Shafai, Tirmizi, Nasai, ibne-Maja aur Darmi."
2624,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat karti hain aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kankariyaan maarna aur Safa aur Marwa ke darmiyan saee karna Allah ka zikr qaaim karney ke liye muqarrar kiya gaya hai.'' Tirmizi, Darmi aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. rawahu Tirmizi aur Darmi."
2625,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, ham ne arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! kya ham (Sahaba ki jamaat) aap ke saye ke liye mina mein koi kamra (sayeban) na bana den? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''nahin, Mina pehley pahunch janey waley ke liye oont bithaaney ki jagah hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi, ibne-Maja aur Darmi."
2626,"Hazrat Naafe (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) pehley do jamaron ke paas bahut der tak thehertey, Allah ki kibriyaai (badhaee) bayan kartey, uski tasbih aur tahmeed bayan kartey aur Allah se duayen kartey, lekin wo jamara uqba (badey shetan) ke paas khadey nahin hotey they. rawahu Maalik."
2627,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne namaze-Zohar Zul-Hulaifa ke maqam par ada ki, phir aapney apni oontni mangwai , aapney uski kohan ke daain pehlu par halka sa zakhm lagaya , wahan se khoon bahney laga , aapney wo khoon saaf kar diya aur uski gardan mein do jootey dal diye, phir aap apni sawari par Sawar ho gaey, jab wo Beda mein aap ko lekar sidhi khadi ho gaee to aapney Haj ke liye talbiya pukara. rawahu Muslim."
2628,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik martaba chand bakriyan bator qurbani , Baitullah bhijwaaeen to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen Qalada (haar waghera) pehnaya. muttafaq aleh."
2629,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki taraf se qurbani ke roz eik gaaey zibeh ki. rawahu Muslim."
2630,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney Haj ke moqe par apni paak biviyon (biwiyon) ki taraf se eik gaaey zibeh ki. rawahu Muslim."
2631,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke qurbani ke oonton ke qalaade khud apney haathon se baatey, phir aapney unhen qalaade pahnaaey, unka shiaar kiya aur unhen qurbani ke liye bheja, aur jo chiz aap ke liye halal ki gaee wo aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) par haram nahin hui thi. muttafaq aleh."
2632,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, maine unke qalaade, oon se tayyar kiye jo ke merey paas mojud thi, phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen merey walid ke sath ( Baitullah ( rawana kiya. muttafaq aleh."
2633,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik aadmi ko qurbani ka oont haanktey huey dekha to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''is par Sawar ho ja.'' usney arz kiya : ye to qurbani ka oont hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''is par Sawar ho ja.'' usney arz kiya : ye to qurbani ka oont hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne dusri ya teesri martaba farmaya : ''tujh par afsos ho ! is par sawaar ho ja.'' muttafaq aleh."
2634,"Hazrat Abu-Zubair bayan kartey hain, maine Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, un se qurbani ke oont par sawari ke barey mein sawal kiya gaya to unhoney kaha : maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''jab to is par sawari karney par majbur ho jaey to phir sawari milney tak bhaley tareeqey se is par sawari kar.'' rawahu Muslim."
2635,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik aadmi ke sath qurbani ke sola oont bhejey aur usey un par ameer muqarrar kiya, to usney arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! agar un mein se koi chalney se aajiz aa jaey to phir main kya karun? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''usey nahar (qurban) kar dena aur us (ke qalaadey) ke jootey uskey khoon mein rang kar uskey pehlu par nishan laga dena aur is mein se tum aur tumharey sathi na khaeyn.'' rawahu Muslim."
2636,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham ne Hudebiya ke saal Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath oont aur gaaey ko saat-saat aadmiyon ki taraf se (bator qurbani) nahar (qurban) kiya. rawahu Muslim."
2637,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke wo eik aadmi ke paas aaye jo apney qurbani ke oont ko bitha kar nahar kar raha tha, to unhoney usey farmaya : ''Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki sunnat ke mutabiq isey khada karo aur iski taang ko baandho (phir nahar (qurban) karo). muttafaq aleh."
2638,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey hukm farmaya ke main aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke qurbani ke oonton ki nigrani karun aur unki lagaamon, chamdon aur paalaanon ko sadqa kar dun aur qassaab ko is mein se kuch na dun, farmaya : ''ham usey apney paas se dengey.'' muttafaq aleh."
2639,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham apney qurbani ke oonton ka gosht teen din se zayed nahin khaya kartey they, phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamein rukhsat (chhoot) di to farmaya : ''khaao aur zaade-rah ke taur par sath bhi ley jaao.'' isliye ham ne khaya aur zaade-rah ke taur par sath bhi laye. muttafaq aleh."
2640,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) riwayat kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Hudebiya ke saal qurbani ke janwer bhejey, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke qurbani ke janwaron mein Abu-Jahal ka oont bhi tha jiski naak mein chaandi ka aur eik dusri riwayat mein hai ke soney ka eik kada tha, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) us se mushrekin ko ghussa dilaanaa chahtey they. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
2641,"Hazrat Naajiya Khuzaae (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! qurbani ke oonton mein se koi chalney se aajiz aa jaey to kya karun? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''usey nahar kar dena phir (uske qalaade) ke jootey uskey khoon mein dubo dena (aur uskey pehlu par nishan laga dena) phir usey logon ke liye chhod denaa taake wo usey kha lein.'' rawahu Malik  ,Tirmizi aur ibne-Maja."
2642,Hazrat Abu-Dawood aur Darmi ne usey Naajiya Aslami se riwayat kiya hai. rawahu Abu-Dawood aur Darmi.
2643,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Qart (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ke nazdik sab se azeem din qurbani ka din hai, phir (Mina mein) qarar pakadney (giyara zul-hijja) ka din hai.'' Saur (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya is se qurbani ka doosra din murad hai. raawi bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas paanch ya chhe qurbani ke oont pesh kiye gaey, wo aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke qarib honey lagey ke aap kis se ibtida (shuruat) farmaeyngey. raawi bayan kartey hain : jab wo pahluoon ke bal gir paden to aapney koi halki si baat ki jisey main samajh na saka , to maine (apney paas waley shakhs sey) kaha : aapney kya farmaya hai? usney kaha : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya hai : ''jo shakhs chahey is se gosht kaat kar ley jaey.'' Abu-Dawood, Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) aur Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hadees (Baabul Uzahiya) mein zikr ki gaee hai. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
2644,"Hazrat Salma bin Akwa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum mein se jisney qurbani ki hai. teesrey din ke baad (yani chauthey roz) uskey ghar mein qurbani ka gosht nahin hona chahiye.'' jab aainda saal aaya to Sahaba ne arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! jis tarah ham ne pichley saal kiya tha kya is saal bhi ham wesay hi keren? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''khaao, khaalo aur zakhira bhi karo, kyonkey guzishta saal log qehat (sukha) saali ki wajeh se takleef mein they, isliye maine irada kiya ke tum unki madad karo.'' muttafaq aleh."
2645,"Hazrat Nubesha (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ham ne tumhen mana kiya tha ke qurbani ka gosht teen din se zayed nahin khana taake tumhen kashaaish aur khushhali mil jaey, ab Allah Taala ne tumhen khushhali ata kar di hai to khaao, zakhira karo aur (sadqa karkey) ajr paoo. aur sun lo ! ye dinon (din) khaney peeney aur Allah Taala ka zikr karney ke hain.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
2646,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Hajjatul-wadaa ke moqe par apna sar mundaayaa , aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke baaz Sahaba ne bhi sar mundaayaa aur un mein se baaz ne baal katraaey. muttafaq aleh."
2647,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujhey bataya ke maine Marwa ke paas teer ke bhaal se Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sar ke baal katrey. muttafaq aleh."
2648,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Hajjatul-wadaa ke moqe par farmaya : ''aey Allah ! sar mundaaney walon par rehem farma.'' Sahaba ne arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! aur baal katraaney walon par bhi. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aey Allah ! sar mundaaney walon par rehem farma.'' Sahaba ne arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! baal katraaney walon par bhi. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''baal katraaney walon par bhi.'' muttafaq aleh.
2649,Hazrat Yahya bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) apni daadi se riwayat kartey hain ke unhoney Hajjatul-wadaa ke moqe par Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko sar mundwaaney walon ke liye teen baar aur baal katraaney walon ke liye eik baar dua kartey huey suna. rawahu Muslim.
2650,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Mina tashrif laye to jamara par aaye aur usey kankariyaan maarin, phir Mina main apni rihaaish gaah par aaye aur qurbani ki phir aapney hajjaam ko mangaayaa aur aapney apney sar ki daain taraf hajjaam ki taraf ki to usney usey moond diya phir aapney Abu-Talha Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) ko bulaya aur wo baal unhen dey diye, phir aapney baain janib uski taraf ki aur farmaya : ''moond do.'' to usney usey moond diya to aapney wo baal bhi Abu-Talha ko dey diye aur farmaya : ''inhen logon mein taqseem kar do.'' muttafaq aleh."
2651,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko ehram baandhney se pehley aur qurbani ke din Baitullah ka tawaf karney se pehley kastoori ki milawat wali khushbu lagaya karti thi. muttafaq aleh."
2652,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne qurbani ke din tawafe ifaaza kiya, phir wapis tashrif laye aur Zohar ki Namaz Mina mein ada ki . rawahu Muslim."
2653,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) aur Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne aurton ko sar mundaaney se mana farmaya. rawahu Tirmizi."
2654,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aurton par sar mundaanaa wajib nahin, un par baal katrana wajib hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood, Tirmizi aur Darmi."
2655,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Hajjatul-wadaa ke moqe par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne logon ki khatir Mina mein waquf farmaya , log aap ke paas aatey aur masayel daryaft kartey , eik aadmi aap ke paas aaya to usney arz kiya : maine la-ilmi mein qurbani se pehley sar mundaa liya? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''qurbani kar lo, koi harj nahin.'' phir eik aur aadmi aaya to usney arz kiya : maine kankariyaan maarney se pehley la ilmi mein qurbani kar li hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''(ab) kankariyaan maar lo, koi harj nahin.'' Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se jis chiz ki bhi taqdeem aur takheer (pahal karne aur deri) ke barey mein sawal kiya gaya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne yehi farmaya : ''ab kar lo, koi harj nahin.'' Bukhari , Muslim. aur Muslim ki riwayat mein hai : eik aadmi aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aaya to usney arz kiya, maine kankariyaan maarney se pehley sar moond liya hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ab kankariyaan maar lo, koi harj nahin.'' phir eik aur aadmi aaya, usney arz kiya, maine kankariyaan maarney se pehley tawafe-ifaaza kar liya? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ab kankariyaan maar lo, koi harj nahin.'' muttafaq aleh."
2656,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, qurbani ke din Mina mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se masayel daryaft kiye gaey to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) yehi farma rahey they : ''koi harj nahin.'' eik aadmi ne aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se masla puchha to usney arz kiya : maine ghurub aaftaab ke baad kankariyaan maari hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''koi harj nahin.'' Bukhari."
2657,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik aadmi aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aaya to usney arz kiya : ''Allah ke Rasool ! maine sar mundaaney se pehley tawafe-ifaaza kar liya hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ab sar mundaa lo ya baal katra lo, koi harj nahin.'' phir eik doosra aadmi aaya to usney arz kiya, maine kankariyaan maarney se pehley qurbani kar li? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ab kankariyaan maar lo, koi harj nahin.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
2658,"Hazrat Usama bin Shareek (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main Haj karney ke liye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath rawana hua, log aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aatey aur masayel daryaft kartey they, kisi ne kaha : Allah ke Rasool ! maine tawaf karney se pehley saee kar li, ya maine eik chiz ko muakhkhar kar liya ya maine koi chiz muqaddam kar li , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farmatey they : ''us shakhs ke siwa jisney kisi musalman ki izzat ko kharab kiya, koi harj nahin, aisa shakhs zalim hai aur aisa shakhs hi harj , gunah aur halakat ka shikar hua.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
2659,"Hazrat Abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne qurbani ke din hamein khitab farmaya to farmaya : ''zamana (saal) ghoom-ghumaa kar usi surat par aa gaya hai jaisey us din tha, jis roz Allah Taala ne zamin aur aasman takhleeq farmaai they, saal baara maah ka hai, un mein se chaar hurmat waley hain, teen , zul-Qada , zul-hijja aur Mohrim to mutawatir (lagatar) hain aur rajab Muzar jo ke jamaa-dussani aur Shoban ke darmiyan hai.'' aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye kon sa mahina hai? '' ham ne arz kya : Allah aur uskey Rasool behtar jantey hain, aapney khamoshi ikhtiyar kar li yahan tak ke ham ne khayal kiya aap iska koi aur naam rakhengey , phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya ye zul-hijja nahin?'' ham ne arz kiya, ji haan ! aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye kon sa shehar hai? ''ham ne arz kiya, Allah aur uskey Rasool behtar jantey hain, aap khamosh rahey yahan tak ke ham ne khayal kiya ke aap iska koi aur naam rakhengey , phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya ye Balda (yani Makka ( nahin ?'' ham ne arz kiya, ji haan , aisey hi hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye kon sa din hai? '' ham ne arz kya Allah aur uskey Rasool behtar jantey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khamosh rahey yahan tak ke ham ne guman kiya ke aap iska koi aur naam rakhengey , phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya ye qurbani ka din nahin?'' ham ne arz kiya, ji haan , aisey hi hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tumharey khoon , tumharey amwaal aur tumhari izzatein tum par is maah mein, is shehar mein aur is din ki hurmat ki tarah tum par haram hain, tum an-qareeb apney rab se mulaqat karney waley ho, wo tumharey aamaal ke barey main tum se sawal kerega, sun lo ! tum merey baad gumrah na ho jana ke eik doosrey ko qatl karney lago , sun lo ! kya maine tum tak (deen) pahuncha diya?'' unhoney arz kiya : ji haan , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aey Allah ! gawah rehna , jo yahan mojud hain wo ghair mojud tak pahuncha den, kabhi kabhi jis ko baat pahunchaai jati hai wo sunney waley se ziyada yad rakhney wala hota hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
2660,"Hazrat Vabra (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha : main kis waqt kankariyaan maarun? unhoney farmaya : jab tumhara Imam kankariyaan maarey to tum bhi kankariyaan maaro. maine dobara un se puchha to unhoney farmaya : ham intizar kartey rehtey they, jab Suraj dhal jata to ham kankariyaan maartay they. Bukhari."
2661,"Hazrat Salim (Raziallahu anhu) ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain ke wo jamara duniya (masjide-khafeef ke qarib waley jamara ko) saat kankariyaan maartay aur her kankari ke baad Allahu-Akbar kehtey they, phir aagey badhtey yahan tak ke naram zamin par qibla rukh khadey ho kar der tak haath utha kar duayen kartey , phir baain janib ho kar naram zamin par qibla rukh khadey ho kar haath utha kar der tak duayen kartey rehtey , phir darmiyan waley jamre ko saat kankariyaan maartey jab kankari maartey to Allahu-Akbar kehtey they phir wadi ke nasheb se jamara-aqba ko saat kankariyaan maartey, aap her kankari maartay waqt Allahu-Akbar kehtey, aap uskey paas na thehertey phir wapis aa jatey aur farmatey : maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko isi tarah kartey huey dekha hai. Bukhari."
2662,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Abbas bin Abdul-Muttalib (Raziallahu anhu) ne pani pilaney ki wajeh sey, Mina ki raaten Makka mein guzarney ke liye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se ijazat talab ki to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen ijazat dey di. muttafaq aleh."
2663,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) pani peeney ki jagah par tashrif laye to aapney pani talab kiya to Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : Fazal ! apni walida ke paas jaao aur unke paas se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke liye pani lekar aao . aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mujhey (yahin sey) pilaaoo.'' unhoney arz kiya Allah ke Rasool ! log apney haath is mein daltey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mujhey (yahin sey) pilaaoo.'' aapney usi mein se nosh farmaya , phir aap zam zam par tashrif laye to log wahan pani pila rahey they aur khub mehnat kar rahey they. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kaam kartey raho, kyonkey tum eik nek kaam mein mashghool ho.'' phir farmaya : ''agar log tum par ghalib na aa jaeyn to main bhi apni sawari se utar aata yahan tak ke main rassi is par rakh leta.'' aapney apney kandhey ki taraf ishara farmaya. Bukhari."
2664,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Zohar, Asr, Maghrib aur Ishaa ki namazein padhein , phir aap wadi mohsib mein thodi der soey , phir aap sawari par Baitullah tashrif laye aur uska tawaf (wadaa') kiya. Bukhari."
2665,"Hazrat Abdul-Azeez bin Rafe bayan kartey hain, maine Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se daryaft kiya, maine kaha : agar aapney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se koi baat yad ki ho to mujhey bataeyn ke aapney tarwiya (aath zul-hijja) ke din Zohar ki Namaz kahan padhi thi ? unhoney farmaya : Mina mein , phir puchha : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Mina se wapis aatey huey Asr ki Namaz kahan padhi thi? farmaya : wadi abtah mein , phir farmaya : jaisey tumharey Ameer karen wesay tum karo. muttafaq aleh."
2666,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, abtah mein qiyam karna sunnat nahin, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne to wahan isliye qiyam farmaya tha ke wahan se (Madina ke liye) rawana hona ziyada aasan tha. muttafaq aleh."
2667,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, maine maqam tanaim se Umre ke liye ehram baandha, main (Makka mein) dakhil hui aur apna Umra ada kiya, jabkey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne abtah ke maqam par mera intizar farmaya yahan tak ke main Umre se farigh ho gaee to aapney logon ko kooch ka hukm farmaya. aap wahan se nikley aur Baitullah ka tawaf subah ki Namaz se pehley kiya, phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Madina ke liye rawana huey. maine Sahih Bukhari aur Sahih Muslim ki riwayat ke hawaley se ye hadees nahin pai, balke aakhir par thodey se ikhtilaf ke sath Abu-Dawood ki riwayat mein paya. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
2668,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, log (Mina se farigh ho kar) kisi bhi tareeqe se wapis chaley jatey they, (ye sooratehaal dekh kar) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum mein se koi shakhs Makka se na jaey yahan tak ke uska aakhiri waqt Baitullah ke paas ho, (tawafe-wadaa' karey) albatta haiz wali aurat ko mustashnaa (is-se alag) qarar diya.'' muttafaq aleh."
2669,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, kooch (ke din) ki raat Safiya (Raziallahu anhu) ko haiz aa gaya, to unhoney arz kiya, mera khayal hai ke (tawaf wadaa' ki wajeh sey) maine tumhen rok diya hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''(arab ke muhaawre ke mutabiq) be-aulad, sar mundi ya halaq mein bimari wali, (us se badduaa murad nahin, balke jaisey kaha jata hai : terey haath khaak aalud hon wesay hi ye alfaz hain) kya usney qurbani ke din tawafe-ifaaza kiya tha ?'' aap ko bataya gaya : ji haan, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''phir (Madina ki taraf) kooch karo.'' muttafaq aleh."
2670,"Hazrat Amr bin Ahwas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko Hajjatul-wadaa ke moqe par farmatey huey suna : ''aaj kon sa din hai? ''Sahaba ne arz kiya : Hajje-Akbar ka din hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tumharey amwaal aur tumhari izzatein tumharey darmiyan is shehar mein , tumharey s din ki hurmat ki tarah haram hain, sun lo ! koi zalim apni jaan par zulm na karey, sun lo ! koi zalim apni aulad par zulm na karey na bachcha apney walid par zulm karey, sun lo ! shetan is baat se hamesha ke liye mayus ho chuka hai ke uski tumharey is shehar mein ibadat ho, lekin tumharey aisey umur (baton) mein jinhen tum maamuli samajhtey ho, uski itaat hogi to wo is par hi razi ho jaeyga.'' ibne-Maja , Tirmizi . aur unhoney isey sahih qarar diya hai. ba-snaad rawahu Tirmizi aur ibne-Maja."
2671,"Hazrat Raafe bin Amr Muzni (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko Mina mein chaasht ke baad siyahi maael safed khachchar par logon se khitab kartey huey suna, jabkey Ali (Raziallahu anhu) aap ki taraf se logon tak baat pahuncha rahey they jabkey log kuchh khadey they aur kuchh bethey huey they. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
2672,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) aur ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne qurbani ke din tawafe-ziyaarat ko raat tak muakhkhar (deri) farmaya. rawahu Tirmizi, Abu-Dawood aur ibne-Maja."
2673,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne tawafe-ifaaza ke saton chakkaron mein ramal nahin farmaya. rawahu Abu-Dawood aur ibne-Maja.
2674,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi jamara aqbaa ko kankariyaan maar ley to biwiyon ke (sath jima ke) siwa uskey liye her chiz halal ho jati hai.'' Sharahus-sunnah. aur unhoney farmaya : iski sanad zaeef hai. rawahu Sharahus-sunnah.
2675,"Hazrat Ahmed aur Nasai ki ibne-Abbas se marwi (bayan) riwayat mein hai, farmaya : ''jab wo kankariyaan maar ley to biwiyon ke ilawa her chiz is par halal ho jati hai.'' rawahu Ahmed aur Nasai."
2676,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne din ke pichhley pahar jab aapney Namaze-Zohar ada ki to tawafe-ifaaza kiya, phir aap Mina wapis tashrif ley aaye , aapney ayyaame-tashreeq ki raaten wahan guzaarein, jab Suraj dhal jata to aap her jamara ko saat saat kankariyaan maartay, her kankari ke sath Allahu-Akbar kehtey, pehley aur doosrey jamre ke paas khadey hotey , lamba qiyam farmatey aur narmi aur aajizi ke sath duayen kartey , aur aap teesrey ko kankariyaan maartay aur uskey paas khadey nahin hotey they. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
2677,"Hazrat Abul-Badaah bin Aasim bin Adi apney walid se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney farmaya , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne oonton ke charwaahon ko raat basar karney ki rukhsat (choot) de-di ke wo qurbani ke din ko kankariyaan maaren phir qurbani ke din ke baad wo do din ki rami ko jama kar lein aur eik din main hi kankariyaan maar lein. Maalik , Tirmizi Nasai. aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees sahih hai. rawahu Malik, Tirmizi aur Nasai."
2678,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke kisi aadmi ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se puchha ke ehram wala kon se kapdey pehan sakta hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''qameez , amaamey , shalwaarein , jubbey , aur mozey na pahno , albatta agar koi shakhs jootey na paey to wo mozey pehan ley aur unhen takhnon ke nichey tak kaat ley aur aisa koi kapda na pahno jisey Zaafran aur waras ki khushbu lagi ho.'' Bukhari, Muslim. muttafaq aleh. aur Imam Bukhari ne eik dusri riwayat mein ye izafa naqal kiya hai : ''ehram wali aurat nqaab pehney na dastaane.''"
2679,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko khitab kartey huey suna, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farma rahey they : ''jab Mohrim jootey na paey to wo mozey pehan ley aur jab wo tehband na paey to shalwaar pehan ley.'' muttafaq aleh."
2680,"Hazrat Yala bin Umayya (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham Jaarana mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas they jab eik Erabi (dehati) (dehaati) aap ke paas aaya usney jubba pehan rakha tha aur usney Zaafran ki bani hui khushbu bhi khub laga rakhi thi, usney arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! maine Umre ka ehram baandha hai aur maine ye (jubba) pehan rakha hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''rahi khushbu jo tum ne laga rakhi hai usey teen martaba dho do, aur raha jubba to usey utaar do, aur phir apney Umerey mein wesay hi kar jaisey to apney Haj mein karta hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
2681,"Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mahram apna nikah karey na kisi ka nikah kiraaey aur na hi peghame-nikah bhejey.'' rawahu Muslim."
2682,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) riwayat kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne haalate-ehram mein Memuna (Raziallahu anhu) se nikah kiya. muttafaq aleh.
2683,"Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anhu) ke bhaanjey Yazid bin As'amm, Memuna (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne un se shaadi ki to aap Mohrim nahin they. Al-Sheikh Imam Muhiussunnah (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, aksar muhaddeseen ka ye mauqif hai ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne un se shaadi ki to aap Mohrim nahin they jabkey aapney haalate-ehram mein is mamley ko zahir farmaya. phir aapney Makka ke raastey mein maqame-sarf par un se khilwat ikhtiyar ki, jabkey aap haalate-ehram mein nahin they. rawahu Muslim."
2684,Hazrat Abu-Ayub (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) haalate-ehram mein apna sar dho liya kartey they. muttafaq aleh.
2685,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne haalate-ehram mein pachhney lagwaaey. muttafaq aleh.
2686,"Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ne us aadmi ke barey mein jiski haalate-ehram mein aankhen dukhti hon, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se hadees bayan ki ke wo apni aakhon par musbir ka lep kar sakta hai. rawahu Muslim."
2687,"Hazrat Umme-Husain (Raziallahu anhu) bayan karti hain, maine Usama (Raziallahu anhu) aur Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ko dekha ke un mein se eik Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki oontni ki mahaar (lagaam) thaamey huey tha jabkey doosra (chhatri ki tarah) apna kapda buland kiye , aap ko garmi se bachaney ke liye , aap par saya kiye huey tha yahan tak ke aapney jamara-aqbaa ko kankariyaan maar lein  rawahu Muslim."
2688,"Hazrat Kab bin Ajra (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke main Hudebiya ke maqam par tha ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) merey paas se guzrey, maine ehram baandh rakha tha aur handiya ke nichey aag jala raha tha jabkey juein merey chehrey par gir rahi thin, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tumhari juein tumhen takleef deti hain?'' maine arz kiya, ji haan. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''apna sar mundaa lo aur chhe miskinon ko eik farq (taqreeban saat kilo) anaj do ya teen rozey rakho ya eik bakri zibeh karo.'' muttafaq aleh."
2689,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko aurton ko haalate-ehram mein dastane pehanney, naqaab karney aur waras aur Zaafran se rang kiye huey kapdey pehanney se mana farmatey huey suna, uskey ilawa , wo zard rang ke ya resham ke baney huey jo kapdey chahen pehan lein, ya zewar, shalwaar, qameez aur mozey pehan sakti hain. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
2690,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath ehram baandhey huey they, sawar hamarey paas se guzartey to ham apni chadaren sar se chehrey par latka letin aur jab wo hamarey paas se guzar jatey to ham chehron se chadaren utha letin thin. Abu-Dawood. aur ibne-Maja mein is maana ki riwayat hai, rawahu Abu-Dawood aur ibne-Maja ."
2691,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) haalate-ehram mein apney sar par aisa tel laga liya kartey they jis mein khushbu nahin hoti thi. rawahu Tirmizi.
2692,"Hazrat Naafe se riwayat hai ke ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne thandak mehsus ki to farmaya : Naafe ! mujh par koi kapda dalo , maine eik jubba un par dal diya to unhoney farmaya : tum mujh par ye dal rahey ho halanke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Mohrim ko isey pehanney se mana farmaya hai. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
2693,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Malik bin Buhena (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne haalate-ehram mein lahee-jamal ke maqam (Makka aur Madina ke darmiyan eik maqam) par apney sar ke wast (beech) mein pachhney lagwaaey. muttafaq aleh."
2694,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne haalate-ehram mein paaon ki pusht par takleef ki wajeh se pachhney lagwaaey. rawahu Abu-Dawood aur Nasai."
2695,"Hazrat Abu-Raafe (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Memuna (Raziallahu anhu) se shaadi ki to aap haalate-ehram mein nahin they, aur jab aapney un se khilwat ki tab bhi aap haalate-ehram mein nahin they, aur main dono ke darmiyan qaasid aur wasta tha. Ahmed, Tirmizi . aur farmaya : ye hadees Hasan hai. rawahu Ahmed aur Tirmizi."
2696,"Hazrat Sa'ab bin jasaama (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney maqame-abwaa ya maqame-vadaan par eik jangli gadhaa Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein pesh kiya aapney usey qubul na farmaya , jab aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uskey chehrey par afsurdagi ke aasaar dekhey to farmaya : ''ham ne isliye tumhen wapis kiya hai ke ham haalate-ehram mein hain.'' muttafaq aleh."
2697,"Hazrat Abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke wo (Hudebiya ke saal) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath rawana huey to wo apney baaz sathiyon ke sath peechey reh gaey, wo haalate-ehram mein they jabkey wo khud haalate-ehram mein nahin they, unhoney merey dekhney se pehley eik jangli gadhaa dekha, jab unhoney usey dekha to unhoney usey chhod diya yahan tak ke Abu-Qatada ne usey dekh liya , wo apney ghodey par Sawar hua aur un (apney sathiyon) se mutalba kiya ke wo usey uska kodaa pakda den lekin unhoney inkar kar diya, unhoney khud usey liya aur is par hamla kar diya aur usey zakhmi kar diya, phir unhoney aur unke sathiyon ne usey khaya , lekin unhen nadaamat aur pareshani hui, jab wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas pahunchey to unhoney aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se masla daryaft kiya, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya uska koi hissey tumharey paas hai? '' unhoney arz kiya : uska eik paaon hamarey paas hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey liya aur usey khaya. aur Sahih Bukhari aur Sahih Muslim ki dusri riwayat mein hai : jab wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aaye to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tum mein se kisi ne usey kaha tha ke is par hamla karo? ya uski taraf ishara kiya ho?'' unhoney arz kiya, nahin, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''uska jo gosht baqi bacha hai usey khaao.'' muttafaq aleh."
2698,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''paanch chizen aisi hain jinhen Haram mein haalate-ehram mein qatl kar deney par koi gunah nahin : chuhiyaa , kawwa , cheel , bichho aur kaatney wala kutta.'' muttafaq aleh."
2699,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat karti hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''paanch qism ke janwer fasiq (nuqsan deh) hain, unhen halal aur Haram her haalat mein qatl kiya jaeyga, sanp , kawwa jo siyah w safed ho, chuhiyaa , kaatney wala kutta aur cheel .'' muttafaq aleh."
2700,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ki Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''is shikar ka gosht tumharey liye haalate-ehram mein halal hai jisey tum ne shikar kiya ho na wo tumhari khatir shikar kiya gaya ho.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood, Tirmizi aur Nasai."
2701,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tiddi (makdi) samandari shikar ke khaane mein hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood aur Tirmizi."
2702,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mehram cheer phaad karney waley darindey ko maar sakta hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood aur ibne-Maja."
2703,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Abi Ammar bayan kartey hain, maine Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se bijju ke barey mein sawal kiya wo shikar hai? unhoney kaha : haan , maine kaha : kya wo khaya jata hai? unhoney kaha : haan, maine kaha : aapney usey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna hai? unhoney kaha : haan , Tirmizi, Nasai , Shafai. aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. rawahu Tirmizi aur Nasai."
2704,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine bijju khaney ke barey mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se daryaft kiya, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''wo shikar hai, aur jab Mohrim uska shikar karey to uskey badley is par eik mendhaa hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood, ibne-Maja aur Darmi."
2705,"Hazrat Khuzaima bin Juzai (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain maine bijju khaney ke barey mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se puchha to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya koi bijju bhi khata hai? ''maine aap se bhediya khaney ke barey mein sawal kiya, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya koi sahibe eman bhediya bhi khata hai? ''Tirmizi. aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : iski sanad qawi nahin. rawahu Tirmizi."
2706,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Usman Taimi bayan kartey hain, ham Talha bin Ubaidullah (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath they aur ham haalate-ehram mein they, un (Talha (Raziallahu anhu)) ko eik (bhuna hua) perinda bator hadiya bheja gaya jabkey Talha so rahey they. ham mein se kuchh ne kha liya aur kuchh ne perhez kiya, to jab Talha (Raziallahu anhu) bedaar huey to unhoney usey khaney walon ki muwaafiqat ki aur farmaya : ham ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath khaya tha. rawahu Muslim."
2707,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, (suleh Hudebiya ke saal) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko (Umra karney sey) rok diya gaya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apna sar mundaayaa , apni paak biviyon (biwiyon) se jima (sambhog) kiya aur qurbani ki, aur phir agley saal Umra kiya. Bukhari."
2708,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath (Umra karney ke liye) rawana huey to Quraish Baitullah pahunchney se pehley haael (rukawat) ho gaey to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apni qurbaaniyaan zibeh kin, aur aapney apna sar mundaayaa jabkey aap ke baaz Sahaba ne sar ke baal katraaey. Bukhari."
2709,Hazrat Miswar bin Makhrima (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne sar mundaaney se pehley qurbani ki aur aapney apney Sahaba ko bhi uska hukm farmaya. Bukhari.
2710,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney kaha : kya tumharey liye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki sunnat kafi nahin ! agar tum mein se kisi ko Haj se rok diya jaey to wo Baitullah ka tawaf karey aur Safa Marwa ki saee karey, phir her chiz se halal ho jaey (ehram ki pabandi khatam ho jaey) yahan tak ke agley saal Haj karey aur qurbani karey, agar qurbani muyassar na ho to phir rozey rakhey. Bukhari."
2711,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Zabaa binte Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas gaey to un se farmaya : ''shayad ke aapney Haj ka irada kiya hai?'' unhoney arz kiya : Allah ki qism ! mujhey kuchh takleef hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen farmaya : ''Hajj karen aur shart qaaim kar lein, is tarah kahin : aey Allah ! merey halal honey ki jagah wohi hogi jahan to mujhey (takleef ki wajeh se aagey janey sey) rok lega.'' muttafaq aleh."
2712,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney Sahaba ko hukm farmaya ke unhoney Hudebiya ke saal jo qurbani ki thi uskey badley mein ab qazae-umre mein qurbani karen. Abu-Dawood. is mein qissa hai aur iski sanad mein Muhammad bin Is-haq (Mudallis (hadees ka wo raawi jo ye zikr na kare ye hadees kis se suni hai)) hai. rawahu Abu-Dawood.
2713,"Hazrat Hujjaj bin Amr Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ki haddi toot jaey ya wo langdaa ho jaey to wo halal ho gaya aur wo agley saal Haj karey.'' Tirmizi, Abu-Dawud, Nasai , ibne-Maja , Darmi . aur Abu-Dawood ne eik dusri riwayat mein izafa naqal kiya hai : ''ya wo bimar ho jaey.'' aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees Hasan hai. aur masaabeh mein zaeef hai. rawahu Tirmizi, Abu-Dawood, Nasai, ibne-Maja aur Darmi."
2714,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Yaamar Dailee (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''Hajj wuqoofe-Arafat hi hai, jo shakhs Muzdalfa ki raat tulu Fajr se pehley Arfa mein qiyam kar ley to usney Haj pa liya, aur Mina ke dinon teen hain, jo shakhs do din mein jaldi karkey farigh ho jaey to is par koi gunah nahin aur jo shakhs takheer karey is par bhi koi gunah nahin.'' Tirmizi, Abu-Dawud, Nasai , ibne-Maja , Darmi aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. rawahu Tirmizi, Abu-Dawood, Nasai, ibne-Maja aur Darmi."
2715,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Fateh Makka ke din farmaya : ''ab hijrat baqi nahin rahi, lekin jihad aur niyat baqi hai, jab tumhen jihad ke liye nikalney ka hukm diya jaey to niklo.'' aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Fateh Makka ke din farmaya : ''Allah ne is shehar ko zamin aur aasman ki takhleeq ke roz hi haram qarar dey diya tha, wo Allah ki hurmat ki wajeh se roze-qiyamat tak haram hai aur Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se pehley is mein qitaal karna halal nahin kiya gaya, aur merey liye bhi din ke kucch waqt ke liye halal kiya gaya, wo Allah ki hurmat ke baais roze-qiyamat tak ke liye haram hai. iska kaanta kaataa jaey na iska shikar bhagaayaa jaey, aur na hi iski giri padi chiz uthai jaey siwaye us shakhs ke jo uska aelan karey, aur na hi uski ghaas kaati jaey.'' Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool !  izkhir (ghaas) ke alawa, kyonkey wo lohaaron aur unke gharon ke istimal ki chiz hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''izkhir (ghaas) ke alawa .'' muttafaq aleh."
2716,Aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki riwayat mein hai : ''uska darkht kaataa jaey na uski giri padi chiz uthai jaey siwaye us shakhs ke jo us chiz ka aelan karey.'' muttafaq aleh.
2717,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''Makka mein aslaha utha kar chalna kisi ke liye bhi halal nahin.'' rawahu Muslim."
2718,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Fateh Makka ke roz Makka mein dakhil huey to aap ke sar par khud tha, jab aapney usey utara to kisi aadmi ne aa kar bataya ke ibne Khatal ghilafe-Kaaba ke sath chimta hua hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''usey qatl kar do.'' muttafaq aleh."
2719,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Fateh Makka ke roz (Makka mein) dakhil huey to aap ke sar par siyah amama tha aur aap haalate-ehram mein nahin they. rawahu Muslim.
2720,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''eik lashkar Kaba par hamla karney ka qasd (irada) (irada) kerega. jab wo Beda ke maqam par hongey to unke awwal aur aakhir tamam faujiyon ko zamin mein dhansa diya jaeyga.'' maine arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! unke awwal aur aakhir ko kaisey dhansa diya jaeyga, jabkey un mein unki riaayaa bhi hogi, aur aisey log bhi hongey jo un mein se nahin hongey, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''unke awwal aur aakhir sab ko dhansa diya jaeyga aur phir unhen unki niyaton ke mutabiq uthaya jaeyga.'' muttafaq aleh."
2721,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''bareek pindliyon wala eik Habshi shakhs Kaba ko barbad kerega.'' muttafaq aleh."
2722,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''goya mein us siyah faam (rang) shakhs ko dekh raha hun jo Kaba ka eik eik pathar ukhaad phenkeyga.'' Bukhari."
2723,Hazrat Yala bin Umayya (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Haram mein zakhira andozi karna ilhaad (khudaa ka inkaar) hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood.
2724,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Makka se farmaya : ''merey nazdik to sab se achchhaa aur sab se pasandida shehar hai, agar meri qom mujhey tujh se na nikaalti to main terey siwa kahin aur na rehta.'' Tirmizi aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai aur iski sanad gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
2725,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Adi bin Humraa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko hazura ke maqam par khadey huey dekha aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farma rahey they : ''Allah ki qism ! to Allah ki zamin ka sab se behtareen tukda aur Allah ki sari zamin se Allah ko sab se ziyada mehbub hai, agar mujhey tujh se nikala na jata to main kabhi na nikalta.'' rawahu Tirmizi aur ibne-Maja."
2726,"Hazrat Abu-Shuraih Adwi (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke unhoney Amr bin Saeed sey, jabke wo Makka ki taraf lashkar rawana kar raha tha, kaha : Janab ameer ! agar tum mujhey ijazat do to main tumhen eik hadees bayan karta hun jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Fateh Makka ke agley roz bayan farmaee thi, jisey merey kanon ne suna, merey dil ne usey yad kiya aur meri aakhon ne usey dekha, jab aapney wo hadees bayan ki to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Allah ki hamd w sanaa bayan ki, phir farmaya : ''be-shak Makka aisi jagah hai jisey Allah ne haram qarar diya hai, aur usey kai logon ne haram qarar nahin diya, jo shakhs Allah aur yoame-aakhirat par eman rakhta hai uskey liye halal nahin ke wo is mein khoon-rezi karey aur uskey darkht kaatey , haan agar koi shakhs is mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke qitaal karney se qitaal ki ijazat aur rukhsat (chhoot) ley to usey kaho : be-shak Allah ne apney Rasool ko uski ijazat di thi aur tumhen ijazat nahin di aur mujhey bhi eik din ke kuchh hissey ke liye ijazat di gaee thi aur iski hurmat aaj bhi wesay hi hai jaisey kal thi, aur chahiye ke jo yahan mojud hai wo ghair mojud tak ye baaten pahuncha dey.'' Abu-Shuraih (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha gaya ke Amr ne tumhen kya jawab diya? unhoney kaha : usney mujhey kaha : Abu-Shuraih ! main isey tum se ziyada janta hun be-shak Haram kisi gunah gaar ko panah deta hai na kisi farar qatil ko aur na hi kisi farar chor ko panah deta hai.'' Bukhari , Muslim. aur Sahih Bukhari mein hai ke الخربۃ ka maana الجنایہ (qusur) hai. muttafaq aleh."
2727,"Hazrat Ayash bin Abi Rabeea Makhzumi (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye ummat khair aur bhalai par qaaim rahegi jab tak ye is hurmat (Makka mukarrma) ki uski tazeem ke mutabiq uski tazeem karti rahegi, jab wo isko zaya karengey to halak ho jaeyngey.'' rawahu ibne-Maja."
2728,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se sirf Quran aur jo kuchh us sahifey mein hai wo likha hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Madina eir se Saur tak Haram hai, jo shakhs is mein koi bidat ejaad karey ya kisi bidat ejaad karney waley ko panah dey to is par Allah Taala , tamam farishton aur tamam logon ki lanat hai, uski nafli-ibadat qubul hogi na farz. musalmanon ki aman eik hi hai, aur is mein adnaa musalman ki aman ki bhi barabar haisiyat hai, jo shakhs kisi musalman ke ehad ko todey to is par Allah , farishton aur tamam logon ki lanat hai, uska nafl qubul hoga na farz , aur jo shakhs apney malikon ki ijazat ke baghair kisi qom se muahida kar ley to is par Allah , farishton aur tamam logon ki lanat hai, aur uska nafl qubul hoga na farz.'' aur Sahee-hain hi ki riwayat mein hai : ''jo shakhs apney aap ko baap ke siwa kisi aur ki taraf mansub kar ley ya apney malikon ke ilawa kisi aur se muahida kar ley to is par Allah , farishton aur tamam logon ki lanat hai, us se nafl qubul hoga na farz.'' muttafaq aleh."
2729,"Hazrat Saad (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main Madina ke dono pathreeley maqaamon ke darmiyani hissey ko Haram qarar deta hun, aur us ilaqey ka darkht kaatna ya uska shikar qatl karna haram hai.'' aur farmaya : ''Madina unke liye behtar hai kaash! ke wo jantey, agar koi shakhs us se adam raghbat ki wajeh se usey chhod jaeyga to Allah usmein uskey badle mein aisey shakhs ko abaad kerega, jo us se behtar hoga, aur jo shakhs uski bhook aur takleef par sabr kerega to roze-qiyamat mein uski sifarish karunga ya mein uskey haq mein gawahi dunga.'' rawahu Muslim."
2730,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''meri ummat mein se jo shakhs Madina ki bhook aur uski takleef par sabr kerega to roze-qiyamat mein uski sifarish karunga.'' rawahu Muslim.
2731,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab log pehla-pehla phal dekhtey to usey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein pesh kartey , jab aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) usey pakad letey to dua farmatey : ''aey Allah ! hamarey liye phalon mein barkat farma , aey Allah ! hamarey liye hamarey Madiney mein barkat farma , hamarey saa aur hamarey mud ( naap tol ke pemaney ( mein barkat farma , aey Allah ! be-shak Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) terey bandey , terey khaleel aur terey Nabi they, aur main bhi tera banda aur tera Nabi hun, be-shak unhoney tujh se Makka ke liye dua farmaee aur main tujh se usi jaisi Madine ke liye dua karta hun aur uski jaisi uskey sath mazeed dua karta hun.'' raawi bayan kartey hain, phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apney kisi sab se chhotey bachchey ko bulatey aur wo phal usey dey detey. rawahu Muslim."
2732,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' be-shak Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) ne Makka ko haram qarar diya aur uski hurmat ko Sabit kiya, aur main Madina ko , uskey do pahadon ke darmiyani ilaqey ko , haram qarar deta hun ke is mein khoon-rezi ki jaey na qitaal ke liye is mein aslaha uthaya jaey aur na hi chaarey ke ilawa uskey darakhton ke pattey jhaadey jaeyn.'' rawahu Muslim."
2733,"Hazrat Aamir bin Saad (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Saad (bin Abi Waqas (Raziallahu anhu)) mauza aqeeq mein waqey (maujood) apney mehal ki taraf ja rahey they ke unhoney kisi ghulam ko darkht kaat'tey huey ya uskey pattey jhaadtey huey paya to unhoney uska kapda salb kar liya, jab Saad (Raziallahu anhu) wapis (Madina) aaye to ghulam ke Malik unke paas aaye aur un se baat ki ke unhoney ghulam se jo kuchh liya hai wo usey unke ghulam ko ya hamen wapis lautaa den, is par unhon (Saad (Raziallahu anhu)) ne farmaya : Allah ki panah ke main us chiz ko wapis kar dun jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey bator ghanimat ata farmaee hai, aur unhoney unhen wo kapda wapis karney se inkar kar diya. rawahu Muslim."
2734,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Madina tashrif laye to Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) aur Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) bukhar mein mubtala ho gaey, main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aai aur aap ko bataya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aey Allah ! jis tarah hamein Makka mehbub hai is tarah ya us-se bhi ziyada Madina hamein mehbub bana dey aur isey sehat dene wala bana dey, iskey saa aur mud mein hamarey liye barkat farma dey aur iskey bukhar ko muntaqil farma aur isey Johfa bhejdey.'' muttafaq aleh."
2735,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) se Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke Madina ke barey mein khuwab ke mutalliq riwayat hai, (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya) : ''maine eik siyah rang bikhre hue baalon wali aurat ko Madina se nikal kar  ''muhiya'a'' par qiyam kartey huey dekha, maine uski taaweel ki ke Madina ki wabaa ''muhiya'a'' muntaqil kar di gaee hai, aur ''muhiya'a'' Johfa ka hi naam hai.'' Bukhari."
2736,"Hazrat Sufiyan bin Abi Zuhair (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''Yamen Fateh ho jaeyga to kuchh log apney oonton ko tez chalatey huey aaeyngey to wo apney ehle w ayaal aur apney itaat guzar logon ko sawar karkey ley jaeyngey halanke Madina unke liye behtar tha kaash! ke wo jantey , aur Sham Fateh ho jaeyga to kuchh log oonton ko tez chalatey huey aaeyngey to wo apney ehle khana aur jo unki itaat ikhtiyar kar lengey unko sawar karkey ley jaeyngey, halanke Madina unke liye behtar tha kaash! wo jaan letey, aur Iraq Fateh ho jaeyga to kuchh log oonton ko tez daudaatey huey aaeyngey aur wo apney ehle aur ayaal aur apney itaat guzar logon ko sawar karkey ley jaeyngey, jabkey Madina unke liye behtar tha kaash! ke wo jaan letey.'' muttafaq aleh."
2737,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mujhey eik aisi basti mein qiyam karney ka hukm diya gaya jo dusri bastiyon par ghalib aa jaeygi, wo usey yasrab kehtey hain, jabkey wo Madina hai, wo logon ko aisey nikal bahar karti hai jaisey bhatti lohey ki mail kuchail nikal bahar karti hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
2738,"Hazrat Jabir bin Samura (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''be-shak Allah Taala ne Madina ka naam taaba rakha hai.'' rawahu Muslim."
2739,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke eik Erabi (dehati) (dehati) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki baiat ki to us Erabi (dehati) (dehati) ko Madina mein bukhar ho gaya, wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aaya to usney kaha : Muhammad ! (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) meri baiat wapis kar den, lekin Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne inkar kar diya, wo phir aaya aur kaha : meri baiat wapis kar den, lekin aapney inkar farmaya , wo phir aap ke paas aaya to usney kaha : meri baiat tod den, lekin aapney inkar farmaya, wo Erabi (dehati) (dehati) (Madina) se chala gaya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Madina bhatti ki tarah hai ke wo buri chiz ko nikal deta hai jabkey achhi chiz ko wo khalis bana deta hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
2740,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''qiyamat qaaim nahin hogi yahan tak ke Madina burey logon ko nikal bahar kerega jaisey bhatti lohey ki mail kuchail nikal bahar karti hai.'' rawahu Muslim."
2741,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Madina ke daakhili raaston par farishtey pehra detey hain, is mein taaoon dakhil hoga na dajjaal.'' muttafaq aleh."
2742,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Makka aur Madina ke ilawa dajjaal her shehar ko kharab kar daleyga , in dono shehron ke tamam daakhili raaston par farishtey safein baandhen unki hifazat kar rahey hain, wo (dajjaal) shor wali zamin par utreyga , phir Madina apney rehney walon ko teen baar khub jhatka dega to her kafir aur munafiq us (dajjaal) ki taraf nikal jaeyga.'' muttafaq aleh."
2743,"Hazrat Saad (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs ehle Madina se dhoka kerega to wo is tarah pighal jaeyga jaisey namak pani mein ghul jata hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
2744,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) safar se wapis tashrif latey aur Madina ki deewaron par nazar padti to aap Madina se mohabbat ki wajeh se apni oontni ko , aur agar kisi aur sawari par hotey to usey tez daudaatey.'' Bukhari."
2745,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko uhud pahad nazar aaya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye wo pahad hai jo ham se mohabbat karta hai aur ham is se mohabbat kartey hain, aey Allah ! be-shak Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) ne Makka ko haram qarar diya, aur main Madina ke dono pathreelii jagah ke darmiyani ilaqey ko haram qarar deta hun.'' muttafaq aleh."
2746,"Hazrat Sehal bin Saad (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''uhad aisa pahad hai jo ham se mohabbat karta hai aur ham is se mohabbat kartey hain.'' Bukhari."
2747,"Hazrat Suleman (Alaihissalam) bin Abi Abdullah bayan kartey hain, maine Saad bin Abi Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) ko dekha ke unhoney eik aadmi ko pakda jo Haram Madina mein , jis ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Haram qarar diya hai, shikar kar raha tha, unhoney uska kapda salb kar liya , to uskey Malik aap ke paas aaye aur aap se is barey mein baat cheet ki to unhoney farmaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne is Haram ko haraam qarar diya hai aur unhoney farmaya : ''jo shakhs kisi ko is mein shikar karta hua paey to wo uska kapda salb kar ley.'' lihaza main ye rizq tumhen wapis nahin dunga jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey ata kiya hai, lekin agar tum chaho to main uski qeemat tumhen ada kar deta hun. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
2748,"Hazrat Saad (Raziallahu anhu) ke azad karda ghulam Saleh se riwayat hai ke Saad (Raziallahu anhu) ne Madina ke kuchh ghulamon ko Madina ke darkht kaat'tey huey paya to unhoney unka saman ley liya , aur unke malikon se farmaya : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko Madina ke darkht se koi chiz kaatney se mana kartey huey suna, aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs iski koi chiz kaatey to jo shakhs usey pakdey to uska saman usi (pakadney waley) ko milega.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
2749,"Hazrat Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' waj (taaif Taaif ka kuchh ilaaqa) ka shikar karna aur uskey khaardaar darakhton ka kaatna haram hai, Allah ke liye haram kiya gaya hai.'' Abu-Dawood. aur Imam Muhi-u-sunna ne bayan kiya : ''waj'' ke barey mein ulamaa ne farmaya hai ke wo Taaif ka eik ilaaqa hai, aur Khitaabi (Raziallahu anhu) ne : (اَنَّھَا)  ki jagah (اَنَّہ) kaha hai. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
2750,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs Madina mein faut ho sakta ho to usey usi mein faut hona chahiye, kyonkey jo shakhs usi hi mein faut hoga mein uski shafaat karunga.'' Ahmed, Tirmizi. aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai aur iski sanad gharib hai. rawahu Ahmed aur Tirmizi."
2751,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Islaami bastiyon mein se Madina aisi basti hai jo sab se aakhir mein wiran hogi.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
2752,"Hazrat Jarir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''be-shak Allah Taala ne meri taraf ""wahi'' farmaee ke aap un teeno , Madina ya Behrein ya Qinnsareen, mein se jahan bhi qiyam farmaain wo aap ka daarul-hijrat hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
2753,"Hazrat Abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Masih dajjaal ka roab Madina mein dakhil nahin hoga, us roz uskey saat darwazey hongey, aur her darwazey par do farishtey hongey.'' Bukhari."
2754,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne dua farmaee : ''aey Allah ! to ne jitni barkat Makka ko di hai us se dugni Madina ko ata farma.'' muttafaq aleh."
2755,"Aale-Khttab mein se eik aadmi ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kiya, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs qazdan meri ziyaarat ke liye aaye to roze-qiyamat wo merey padaus mein hoga, jo shakhs Madina mein sakunat ikhtiyar karey aur uski mushkilat par sabr karey to roze-qiyamat mein uskey liye gawah banunga ya sifarishi hunga, aur jo Harmain (Makka, Madina) mein kisi jagah faut hua to roze-qiyamat wo aman walon mein se hoga.'' (rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan)."
2756,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) marfoo riwayat bayan kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs Haj karey aur meri maut ke baad meri qabr ki ziyaarat karey to wo us shakhs ki tarah hai jisney meri zindagi mein meri ziyaarat ki.'' Imam Behaqi ne dono riwaayatein Shobil-emaan mein riwayat ki hain. (rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan)."
2757,"Hazrat Yahya bin Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) bethey huey they jabkey Madina main eik qabr khodi ja rahi thi, eik aadmi ne qabr mein jhaankaa to kaha : momin ki bahut buri jagah hai, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum ne bahut buri baat ki hai.'' us aadmi ne arz kiya : mera ye irada nahin tha, maine to ye irada kiya ke Allah ki raah mein shahadat (bistar par marney sey) afzal hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ki raah mein shahadat jaisi to koi chiz hi nahin aur mujhey apni qabr ke liye ye Khit'a zamin puri zamin mein sab se ziyada pasandida hai.'' aapney ye baat teen martaba farmaee. Imam Maalik ne isey mursal riwayat kiya hai. rawahu Maalik."
2758,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan farmaya : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko wadi aqeeq mein farmatey huey suna : ''aaj raat merey rab ki taraf se eik aaney wala merey paas aaya to usney kaha : is Mubarak wadi mein Namaz padhein , aur kahin : Umra Haj mein dakhil ho gaya.'' eik dusri riwayat mein hai : ''aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farmaain : Umra aur Haj ki eik sath niyat ki.'' Bukhari."
